%20and%20one%20that%20%E2%80%9Ccannot%20go%20on%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20the%20warring%20parties%20to%20agree%20to%20pauses%20in%20the%20fighting.%20This%20is%20the%20only%20viable%20option%20to%20get%20relief%20items%20into%20Gaza%20right%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20has%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%20need%20those%20with%20influence%20to%20use%20that%20influence%20to%20ensure%20respect%20for%20the%20rules%20of%20war%2C%20deescalate%20the%20conflict%20and%20avoid%20a%20spillover%2C%E2%80%9D%20Griffiths%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20statement%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EScores%20of%20civilians%20have%20reportedly%20been%20killed%20in%20Gaza%20following%20recent%20attacks%20on%20the%20Jabalia%20refugee%20camp.%20This%20is%20just%20the%20latest%20atrocity%20to%20befall%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20where%20the%20fighting%20has%20entered%20an%20even%20more%20terrifying%20phase%2C%20with%20increasingly%20dreadful%20humanitarian%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOctober%207th%20and%20its%20aftermath%20will%20leave%20indelible%20scars%20on%20the%20lives%20of%20millions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Israel%2C%20a%20nation%20was%20left%20in%20shock%20after%20the%20brutal%20and%20graphic%20killing%20of%20some%201%2C400%20people.%20The%20families%20of%20more%20than%20200%20hostages%20continue%20to%20live%20in%20anguish%2C%20unsure%20about%20the%20fate%2C%20wellbeing%20and%20whereabouts%20of%20their%20loved%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Gaza%2C%20women%2C%20children%20and%20men%20are%20being%20starved%2C%20traumatized%20and%20bombed%20to%20death.%20They%20have%20lost%20all%20faith%20in%20humanity%20and%20all%20hope%20of%20a%20future.%20Their%20despair%20is%20palpable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20the%20death%20toll%20is%20rising.%20Violence%20and%20the%20closure%20of%20checkpoints%20mean%20that%20people%20cannot%20access%20food%2C%20jobs%2C%20health%20care%20and%20other%20essential%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20world%20seems%20unable%2C%20or%20unwilling%2C%20to%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20cannot%20go%20on.%20We%20need%20a%20step%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20the%20hostages%20to%20be%20released%20immediately%20and%20unconditionally.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20the%20essentials%20for%20survival%20%E2%80%93%20particularly%20water%2C%20food%2C%20medicine%20and%20fuel%20%E2%80%93%20safely%2C%20immediately%20and%20at%20scale.%20The%20more%20than%20200%20trucks%20which%20have%20crossed%20into%20Gaza%20so%20far%20following%20painstaking%20negotiations%20offer%20some%20relief%20but%20are%20nowhere%20near%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20the%20warring%20parties%20to%20agree%20to%20pauses%20in%20the%20fighting.%20This%20is%20the%20only%20viable%20option%20to%20get%20relief%20items%20into%20Gaza%20right%20now.%20Repeated%20humanitarian%20pauses%20would%20allow%20us%20to%20provide%20more%20aid%20to%20those%20in%20need%20across%20Gaza%2C%20thus%20alleviating%20people%E2%80%99s%20suffering%20and%20reducing%20the%20risk%20of%20civil%20disorder.%20Such%20pauses%20would%20also%20allow%20the%20sick%20and%20wounded%20to%20seek%20medical%20care%20and%20those%20who%20wish%20to%20flee%20to%20do%20so%20safely.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPut%20simply%2C%20we%20need%20the%20parties%20to%20respect%20their%20obligations%20under%20international%20humanitarian%20law%2C%20including%20by%20taking%20constant%20care%20in%20the%20conduct%20of%20military%20operations%20to%20spare%20civilians%20and%20civilian%20objects.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20we%20need%20those%20with%20influence%20to%20use%20that%20influence%20to%20ensure%20respect%20for%20the%20rules%20of%20war%2C%20deescalate%20the%20conflict%20and%20avoid%20a%20spillover.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFailure%20to%20act%20now%20will%20have%20consequences%20far%20beyond%20the%20region%2C%20because%20this%20is%20a%20global%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A