20the%20promotions%2C%20leaving%20the%20senators%20with%20little%20to%20show%20for%20their%20efforts%20besides%20more%20anger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHistorically%20speaking%2C%20military%20promotions%20have%20sailed%20through%20the%20Senate%20while%20lawmakers%20have%20used%20procedural%20hurdles%20to%20slow%20down%20political%20appointees.%20Wednesday%20night's%20floor%20fight%20was%20based%20on%20Republican%20senators%20asking%20for%20Tuberville's%20unanimous%20consent%20to%20expeditiously%20approve%20the%20promotions%2C%20which%20he%20has%20refused%20to%20grant%20for%20over%20nine%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETuberville%2C%20a%20former%20Auburn%20football%20coach%2C%20has%20argued%20that%20the%20Pentagon%20policy%20allowing%20for%20service%20members%20to%20take%20leave%20if%20they%20want%20to%20receive%20an%20abortion%20is%20illegal.%20The%20Alabama%20Republican%20has%20repeated%20his%20vow%20that%20he%20will%20not%20stop%20blocking%20promotions%20until%20the%20Biden%20administration%20changes%20its%20policy%2C%20which%20Defense%20Secretary%20Lloyd%20Austin%20has%20vowed%20will%20not%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Republican%20lawmakers%20made%20clear%20they%20did%20not%20support%20the%20Pentagon's%20policy%2C%20but%20they%20made%20clear%20that%20their%20patience%20with%20their%20colleague%20has%20run%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESen.%20Dan%20Sullivan%2C%20an%20Alaska%20Republican%20and%20colonel%20in%20the%20US%20Marine%20Reserves%2C%20repeatedly%20called%20the%20opposition%20%26quot%3Bidiotic%26quot%3B%20and%20stressed%20that%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20likely%20enjoyed%20watching%20the%20US%20military%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESen.%20Joni%20Ernst%20of%20Iowa%2C%20who%20serves%20in%20the%20Senate%20GOP%20leadership%2C%20continued%20to%20drive%20home%20her%20perspective%20as%20a%20veteran%20%E2%80%94%20a%20potential%20jab%20at%20Tuberville%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftuberville-do