mes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Fnews%2Fvirat-kohlis-10-centuries-are-the-most-by-any-batter-against-sri-lanka-in-odis-interesting-stats-and-trivia-for-india-vs-sri-lanka-in-odis%2Farticleshow%2F104902493.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Time%20to%20Shut%20the%20Floodgates%20of%20Secret%20Political%20Party%20Funding%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F10170626%2Fsyed-hussaini-HlLno-CSbq8-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20system%20in%20India%20has%20traditionally%20been%20hostile%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20transparency%20in%20electoral%20financing.%20When%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20government%20announced%20the%20launch%20of%20a%20new%20instrument%20of%20political%20party%20funding%20to%20ostensibly%20ensure%20greater%20transparency%20and%20eliminate%20black%20money%20from%20the%20system%2C%20it%20was%20hoped%20that%20the%20issue%20of%20anonymous%20financing%20would%20be%20squarely%20dealt%20with.%20However%2C%20using%20the%20Money%20Bill%20route%20to%20bypass%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20government%20brought%20regressive%20amendments%20to%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Act%2C%20Companies%20Act%2C%20RBI%20Act%20and%20the%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%2C%20to%20introduce%20electoral%20bonds%20which%20allow%20donors%20to%20anonymously%20donate%20unlimited%20amounts%20of%20funds%20to%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Electoral%20Bond%20Scheme%2C%20an%20electoral%20bond%20(EB)%2C%20issued%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20a%20promissory%20note%2C%20can%20be%20bought%20by%20any%20Indian%20citizen%20or%20company%20incorporated%20in%20India.%20The%20scheme%20allows%20parties%20to%20receive%20these%20bonds%20without%20the%20public%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20or%20even%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20knowing%20the%20identity%20of%20donors.%20It%20has%20legitimised%20opacity%20and%20opened