%20content%20slate%20at%20a%20time%20when%20other%20media%20companies%20are%20contracting.%20It's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2Fapple-tv-plus-price-increase%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eraising%20its%20prices%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20%249.99%20a%20month%20from%20%246.99%2C%20to%20support%20additional%20content%20and%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInterviews%20with%20agents%20and%20production%20company%20execs%20who%20have%20been%20briefed%20by%20Apple%20insiders%2C%20along%20with%20two%20leaked%20agency%20documents%20that%20detail%20multiple%20streamers'%20content%20wish%20lists%2C%20paint%20a%20picture%20of%20what%20kinds%20of%20shows%20and%20movies%20the%20tech%20giant%20wants%20as%20it%20beefs%20up%20its%20slate.%20Apple%20hasn't%20responded%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%20(For%20what%20Netflix%20is%20looking%20for%20in%20new%20projects%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-netflix-wants-new-shows-series-bear-squid-game-dahmer-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehere%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20has%20built%20its%20identity%20around%20elevated%20but%20popular%20programming%20featuring%20big%20stars%20and%20themes%20that%20are%20hopeful%2C%20avoiding%20controversial%20topics%20that%20risk%20undermining%20its%20giant%20retail%20business%20at%20home%20and%20abroad%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0a%20mandate%20that's%20produced%20shows%20like%20Jason%20Sudeikis%20hit%20%26quot%3BTed%20Lasso%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BPlatonic%26quot%3B%20starring%20Rose%20Byrne%20and%20Seth%20Rogen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20all%20accounts%2C%20it's%20sticking%20with%20that%20mission%20as%20Hollywood%20rebounds%20after%20a%20months-long%20writers'%20strike%20and%20prepares%20for%20the%20resolution%20of%20the%20ongoing%20actors'%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20definitely%20wants%20commercial%20fare%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20one%20agent%20put%20it%20to%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BNo%20religion%2C%20characters%20smoking%2C%20doing%20drugs.%26quot%3B%20Jon%20Stewart's%20talk%20show%20%26quot%3BThe%20Problem%26quot%3B%20is%20parting%20ways%20with%20Apple%20after%20disagreements%20over%20potential%20show%20topics%20including%20China%20and%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F10%2F19%2Fbusiness%2Fmedia%2Fjon-stewart-the-problem-ends.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20is%20%26quot%3Balways%20looking%26quot%3B%20for%20films%20that%20%26quot%3Bhighlight%20humanity%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20one%20of%20the%20agency%20documents.%20Projects%20can%20be%20across%20genres%20but%20should%20be%20hopeful%20and%20have%20a%20clear%20%26quot%3Bwhy%20now.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BFemale-forward%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Belevated%20YA%26quot%3B%20are%20on%20the%20wish%20list%20for%20films.%20Other%20needs%20are%20comedy%20and%20sci-fi%20%E2%80%94%20think%20%26quot%3BFoundation%2C%26quot%3B%20Apple%20TV%2B's%20sci-fi%20drama%20based%20on%20Isaac%20Asimov's%20novels%2C%20which%20just%20completed%20its%20second%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20Apple%20%26quot%3Bwon't%20do%20down%20the%20middle%20bloody%20horror%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20would%20%26quot%3Blove%26quot%3B%20a%20version%20of%20the%20John%20Krasinski-directed%20sci-fi%20horror%20film%20%26quot%3BA%20Quiet%20Place%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20series%2C%20Apple%20has%20a%20growing%20appetite%20for%20unscripted%2C%20according%20to%20the%20second%20agency%20doc.%20It's%20looking%20for%20projects%20that%20can%20be%20completed%20quickly%2C%20which%20could%20include%20a%20competition%20show%20%E2%80%94%20as%20long%20as%20it%20has%20the%20%26quot%3BApple%20premium%20sheen%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20%26quot%3Bwell%20cast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20become%20an%20ambitious%20player%20in%20live%20sports%2C%20with%20rights%20to%20Major%20League%20Soccer%20and%20Major%20League%20Baseball%2C%20Apple%20is%20also%20looking%20for%20complementary%20unscripted%20sports%20programming%20that%20can%20be%20turned%20around%20quickly.%20Access%20to%20subjects%20is%20valued%2C%20but%20according%20to%20the%20document%2C%20not%20every%20project%20has%20to%20have%20%26quot%3Bincredible%20unprecedented%20access%26quot%3B%20like%20Apple's%20docuseries%20%26quot%3BThe%20Dynasty%2C%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20New%20England%20Patriots%2C%20or%20its%20documentary%20feature%20%26quot%3BStephen%20Curry%3A%20Underrated.%26quot%3B%20The%20streamer%20is%20also%20looking%20to%20%26quot%3Bcrack%20the%20code%20on%20sports%20anthology%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20project%20like%20Netflix's%20%26quot%3BUntold%26quot%3B%20docuseries%20that%20can%20appeal%20to%20sports%20and%20non-sports%20fans%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20side%20hustle%20of%20a%20massive%20retail%20business%2C%20Apple%20TV%2B%20can%20fly%20under%20the%20radar%2C%20insulated%20from%20economic%20pressures%20that%20have%20roiled%20the%20entertainment%20business.%20According%20to%20one%20of%20the%20agency%20docs%2C%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20take%20nine-figure%20swings%20on%20tentpole%20films%20like%20%26quot%3BKillers%20of%20the%20Flower%20Moon%26quot%3B%20and%20Ridley%20Scott's%20%26quot%3BNapoleon%2C%26quot%3B%20both%20positioned%20as%20big%20awards%20contenders%20this%20year.%20(Apple%20TV%2B%20was%20the%20first%20streamer%20to%20win%20the%20best%20picture%20Oscar%2C%20in%202022%2C%20for%20%26quot%3BCODA%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20it%20acquired%20at%20the%20Sundance%20Film%20Festival).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20according%20to%20the%20agent%2C%20even%20Apple%20is%20more%20cost-sensitive%20than%20it%20used%20to%20be%3A%20%26quot%3BThey're%20still%20willing%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20right%20star%2C%20but%20spending%20%2415%20to%20%2418%20million%20per%20episode%20isn't%20going%20to%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article