%20said%20that%20the%20world%20has%20grown%20too%20accustomed%20to%20quick%20victories.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20counteroffensive%20hasn't%20gone%20quite%20as%20it%20planned%2C%20but%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20says%20the%20country's%20wins%20in%20the%20battle%20for%20the%20Black%20Sea%2C%20where%20Russia's%20fleet%20has%20taken%20a%20beating%2C%20are%20worth%20remembering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20penetrating%20the%20Surovikin%20line%20in%20Zaporizhzhia%2C%20the%20offensive%20has%20not%20yielded%20the%20kind%20of%20breakthrough%20Ukraine's%20forces%20need%2C%20and%20the%20territorial%20gains%20against%20fortified%20Russian%20defenses%20have%20been%20minimal.%20Ukraine's%20attacks%20in%20and%20around%20occupied%20Crimea%20could%20be%20the%20biggest%20wins%20it%20gets%20before%20next%20spring.%C2%A0These%20achievements%20are%20not%20trivial%20though%2C%20the%20president%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Zelenskyy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.president.gov.ua%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fuspih-ukrayini-v-bitvi-za-chorne-more-ce-te-sho-bude-v-pidru-86729%5C%22%3Eaddressed%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ukraine%20on%20the%20state%20of%20affairs%20in%20the%20Black%20Sea%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20very%20important%20that%20due%20to%20Ukrainian%20courage%2C%20we%20practically%20push%20the%20Russian%20fleet%20out%20of%20the%20eastern%20part%20of%20the%20Black%20Sea%20%E2%80%93%20Russia%20cannot%20use%20our%20sea%20to%20extend%20its%20aggression%20to%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20as%20it%20did%20with%20Syria.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20situation%20had%20%26quot%3Bfundamentally%20changed%26quot%3B%20from%20Russia's%20use%20of%20the%20Black%20Sea%20and%20Crimea%20for%20its%20intervention%20in%20the%20Syrian%20civil%20war%20in%202015.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20when%20we%20add%20even%20more%20security%20to%20the%20Black%20Sea%2C%20Russia%20will%20lose%20any%20opportunity%20to%20dominate%20this%20area%20and%20spread%20its%20influence%20and%20destructiveness%20to%20other%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Ukrainian%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZelenskyy's%20most%20notable%20comment%2C%20however%2C%20was%20a%20criticism%20of%20the%20offensive%20critics%20and%20a%20reflection%20on%20Ukraine's%20actions%20in%20the%20Black%20Sea%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20full-scale%20aggression%20began%2C%20many%20around%20the%20world%20expected%20Ukraine%20to%20not%20withstand%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20the%20incredible%20things%20our%20people%2C%20our%20soldiers%2C%20are%20doing%20are%20perceived%20as%20a%20given.%20Ukraine's%20success%20in%20the%20battle%20for%20the%20Black%20Sea%20is%20what%20will%20be%20in%20history%20textbooks%2C%20though%20it's%20not%20discussed%20as%20often%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20wins%20in%20the%20Black%20Sea%20%E2%80%94%20including%20but%20not%20limited%20to%20inflicting%20severe%20damage%20on%20a%20key%20Russian%20port%2C%20battering%20fleet%20headquarters%2C%20and%20using%20drone%20boats%20to%20terrorize%20much%20larger%2C%20more%20expensive%20targets%20%E2%80%94%20have%20been%20a%20noteworthy%20success%20story%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20David-versus-Goliath%20narrative%20that's%20persisted%20since%20Kyiv%20resisted%20a%20full-scale%20takeover%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20war.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225801%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20soldiers%20from%20the%2080th%20Air%20Assault%20Brigade%20training%20green%20tactics%2C%20clearing%20trenches%20using%20armored%20personnel%20carriers%2C%20recoilless%20guns%2C%20and%20grenade%20launchers%20in%20the%20training%20area%20in%20Donetsk%20Oblast%2C%20Ukraine%2C%20on%20June%2018%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6495b8ac1465b6001998c062%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223867%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainian%20soldiers%20from%20the%2080th%20Air%20Assault%20Brigade%20training%20g