ng%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fpeople-culture%2Ftrending-china%2Farticle%2F3239279%2Fbloodletting-and-cement-bizarre-breast-cancer-treatment-sparks-probe-fake-china-doctor-who-swindled%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%20(SCMP)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20woman%2C%20surnamed%20Wang%2C%20learned%20that%20her%20mother%20had%20been%20diagnosed%20with%20late-stage%20breast%20cancer%20at%20the%20end%20of%202021.%20Soon%20after%20diagnosis%2C%20the%20two%20women%20were%20introduced%20to%20a%20traditional%20Chinese%20medicine%20doctor%20in%20Wuhan%2C%20who%20claimed%20to%20specialise%20in%20treating%20cancer.%20They%20travelled%20to%20meet%20the%20man%2C%20surnamed%20Yu%2C%20at%20his%20Dongyusanbao%20Tumour%20Research%20Institute%2C%20where%20he%20told%20them%20he%20had%20invented%20a%20medicine%20that%20could%20kill%20cancer%20cells.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ms%20Wang%2C%20Mr%20Yu%20went%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20convince%20the%20two%20women%2C%20showcasing%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20credible%20patent%20documents%20and%20prestigious%20awards%20certificates%20for%20his%20cancer%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFilled%20with%20hope%2C%20Ms%20Wang's%20mother%20immediately%20purchased%20the%20first%20batch%20of%20liquid%20medication%20from%20Mr%20Yu%20at%20a%20cost%20of%2020%2C000%20yuan%20(US%242%2C700)%2C%20which%20he%20assured%20was%20a%20simple%20oral%20remedy.%20Over%20the%20course%20of%20a%20year%2C%20Ms%20Wang%20said%20she%20and%20her%20mother%20flew%20to%20Wuhan%20from%20their%20home%20in%20northeastern%20Liaoning%20province%20six%20times.%20This%20journey%20took%20a%20severe%20financial%20toll%2C%20with%20the%20total%20expenditure%20racing%20over%20200%2C000%20yuan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20giving%20the%20elderly%20woman%20oral%20medication%2C%20Mr%20Yu%20also%20made%20dozens%20of%20injections%20into%20her%20breasts%20to%20make%20her%20lose%20blood%2C%20Ms%20