in%20Bangladesh%20is%20expected%20to%20boost%20cross-border%20trade%2C%20and%20significantly%20reduce%20the%20travel%20time%20between%20Agartala%20and%20Kolkata%20via%20Dhaka.%20When%20fully%20completed%2C%20the%20cross-border%20rail%20link%20will%20cut%20the%20travel%20time%20from%20Kolkata%20to%20Agartala%20from%2036%20hours%20to%2012%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20hailed%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Cross%20Border%20Rail%20Link%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%26quot%3B%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20joy%20that%20we%20have%20come%20together%20again%20to%20celebrate%20the%20successful%20cooperation%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh.%20Our%20relationship%20is%20touching%20new%20highs.%20Together%2C%20we%20have%20achieved%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20what%20has%20not%20been%20achieved%20in%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20projects%20are%20important%20for%20India's%20Look%20East%20Policy%20and%20will%20also%20boost%20connectivity%20to%20the%20northeast%20which%20is%20heavily%20dependent%20on%20the%20narrow%20Chicken's%20Neck%20or%20Siliguri%20Corridor.%20They%20are%20also%20a%20testament%20to%20India's%20commitment%20to%20the%20region%20around%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20with%20organizations%20like%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20Initiative%20for%20Multi-Sectoral%20Technical%20and%20Economic%20Cooperation%20(BIMSTEC)%C2%A0which%20has%20its%20secretariat%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cb%3E'First%20Rail%20Link%20Between%20Northeast%2C%20Bangladesh'%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Agartala-Akhaura%20Rail%20Link%2C%20PM%20Modi%20highlighted%20the%20impact%20of%20these%20projects%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20pandemic%20with%20oxygen%20trains.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20first%20rail%20link%20between%20the%20northeast%20and%20Bangladesh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20focused%20especially%20on%20infrastructure%2C%20connectivity%20and%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20we%20have%20started%20three%20new%20bus%20services.%20We%20have%20connected%20Dhaka%2C%20Shillong%2C%20Agartala%2C%20Guwahati%20and%20Kolkata.%20In%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20we%20have%20started%20three%20new%20railway%20services.%20From%202020%2C%20we%20started%20container%20and%20parcel%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20through%20Chittagong%20and%20the%20Mongla%20Port%2C%20we%20have%20connected%20the%20northeastern%20states%20of%20India.%20Our%20connectivity%20initiative%20worked%20as%20a%20lifeline%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20four%20new%20immigration%20check%20posts%20have%20been%20opened%20on%20the%20India-Bangladesh%20border%20and%20our%20bilateral%20trade%20has%20nearly%20tripled.%20The%20journey%20of%20these%20nine%20years%20has%20made%20us%20reach%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Agartala%20Akhaura%20Railway%20Link%20and%20it%20is%20a%20historic%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cb%3E'Firm%20Cooperation%20Between%20Countries'%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Hasina%20said%20the%20relationship%20between%20Bangladesh%20and%20India%20is%20anchored%20in%20history%20culture%20language%20and%20both%20countries%20share%20values%20of%20secularism%2C%20democracy%2C%20and%20countless%20other%20commonalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20Bangladesh%20attaches%20the%20highest%20importance%20to%20its%20relationship%20with%20India%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20connectivity%2C%20trade%2C%20and%20commerce.%20She%20expressed%20gratitude%20to%20the%20government%20of%20India%20for%20its%20significant%20contribution%20to%20these%20sectors%20and%20also%20extended%20Diwali%20greetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20joint%20inauguration%20of%20these%20projects%20manifests%20the%20firm%20friendship%20and%20collaboration%20between%20our%20two%20countries.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20you%20PM%20Modi%20for%20his%20warm%20hospitality%20during%20my%20visit%20to%20New%20Delhi%20in%20September%202023%20to%20attend%20the%20G20%20Leaders'%20Summit.%20I%20express%20my%20heartfelt%20gratitude%20for%20your%20commitment%20to%20strengthening%20the%20bonds%20of%20friendship%20between%20our%20two%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20for%20jointly%20producing%20the%20biopic%20on%20the%20Father%20of%20the%20Nation%20of%20Bangladesh%20Bangabandhu%20'Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rehman%20-%20Mujib%3A%20The%20Making%20of%20a%20Nation'.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20extend%20my%20deep%20appreciation%20and%20thankfulness%20to%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20collaboration%20in%20the%20connectivity%20and%20power%20sector%20stands%20out%20as%20a%20shining%20example%20of%20our%20cooperation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20at%20the%20inauguration%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Bangladesh%20ties%20are%20crucial%20for%20India's%20Act%20East%20Policy%20and%20these%20projects%20have%20also%20laid%20the%20groundwork%20for%20more%20cooperation%20and%20opening%20of%20passenger%20and%20freight%20routes%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20and%20also%20for%20alternative%20supply%20routes%20for%20northeastern%20states%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698861420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fp68nao9o_modi-sheikh-hasina-ani_625x300_01_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bangladesh-rail-link-agartala-akhuara-will-cut-short-agartala-kolkata-journey-pm-modi-sheikh-hasina-4536746%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20Bangladeshi%20counterpart%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20on%20Wednesday%20jointly%20inaugurated%20three%20projects%20via%20virtual%20mode%2C%20including%20a%20key%20rail%20link%20between%20Tripura's%20Nischintapur%20and%20Gangasagar%20in%20Bangladesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bangladesh-rail-link-agartala-akhuara-will-cut-short-agartala-kolkata-journey-pm-modi-sheikh-hasina-4536746%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bangladesh-rail-link-agartala-akhuara-will-cut-short-agartala-kolkata-journey-pm-modi-sheikh-hasina-4536746%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bangladesh-rail-link-agartala-akhuara-will-cut-short-agartala-kolkata-journey-pm-modi-sheikh-hasina-4536746%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Kemon%20Acho'%20To%20'Kem%20Cho'%2C%20Gujarat%20Minister's%20Unique%20Investment%20Pitch%20In%20Bengal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20the%20similarities%20in%20the%20style%20of%20celebrations%20as%20well%20as%20language%20between%20West%20Bengal%20and%20his%20state%2C%20Gujarat%20Minister%20Harsh%20Sanghavi%20made%20a%20pitch%20for%20investment%20at%20a%20roadshow%20which%20was%20part%20of%20a%20Vibrant%20Gujarat%20event%20in%20Kolkata.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20like%20we%20say%20%3Cem%3Ekem%20cho%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20you%20say%20%3Cem%3Ekemon%20acho%3C%2Fem%3E%20(both%20mean%20%26quot%3Bhow%20are%20you%26quot%3B)%20when%20you%20meet%20someone%20familiar%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sanghavi%20said%2C%20leaving%20the%20audience%20in%20splits.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20gathering%20of%20industry%20representatives%20and%20investors%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20minister%2C%20who%20holds%20the%20Home%20and%20Industries%20portfolios%2C%20among%20others%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20visited%20several%20parts%20of%20West%20Bengal%20and%20I%20have%20seen%20so%20many%20similarities%20between%20Gujarat%20and%20the%20state.%20Gujarat%20and%20Bengal%20can%20march%20ahead%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20interactions%2C%20Mr%20Sanghavi%20shared%20insights%20into%20the%20success%20of%20the%20Vibrant%20Gujarat%20Summit%20and%20emphasised%20that%20Gujarat%20has%20become%20a%20role%20model%20for%20development%20and%20a%20preferred%20investment%20destination%20over%20the%20past%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20highlighted%20Gujarat's%20cumulative%20FDI%20of%20%2455%20billion%20between%202002%20and%202022%2C%20attributing%20the%20state's%20attractiveness%20to%20its%20policy-driven%20approach%2C%20including%20initiatives%20like%20Gujarat%20Renewable%20Policy%202023%2C%20Atmanirbhar%20Gujarat%20Scheme%202022%2C%20Integrated%20Logistics%20and%20Logistics%20Park%20Policy%202021%2C%20Electric%20Vehicle%20Policy%202021%2C%20Tourism%20Policy%2C%20and%20Textile%20Policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Sanghavi%20also%20spoke%20of%20Gujarat's%20industrial%20development%2C%20specifically%20highlighting%20special%20investment%20zones%20such%20as%20Gift%20City%2C%20Dholera%2C%20and%20Mandal-Bechraji%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Petrochemicals%20Investment%20Zones%2C%20Dream%20City%2C%20Sanand%20Manufacturing%20Hub%2C%20Logistics%20Park%2C%20Delhi-Mumbai%20Industrial%20Corridor%2C%20and%20Mumbai-Ahmedabad%20High-Speed%20Rail%20to%20stress%20that%20the%20state%20has%20world-class%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUrging%20investment%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20encouraging%20active%20participation%20in%20the%20nation's%20developmental%20journey%2C%20he%20also%20invited%20the%20audience%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Vibrant%20Gujarat%20Summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Sanghavi's%20pre-scheduled%20visit%20comes%20close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20Tata%20Motors'%20announcement%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20arbitration%20proceedings%20over%20the%20loss%20of%20its%20capital%20investment%20made%20in%20the%20Sing