mate-at-her-noida-flat-arrested-cops-4536698%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThe%20Way%20I%20See%20Things...%26quot%3B%3A%20Suniel%20Shetty%20On%2070-Hour%20Workweek%20Suggestion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EInfosys%20founder%20Narayana%20Murthy%20created%20a%20social%20media%20stir%20after%20suggesting%20that%20India's%20youngsters%20must%20work%20for%2070%20hours%20every%20week%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20boost%20the%20country's%20overall%20work%20productivity.%20His%20remarks%20sparked%20a%20national%20debate%20and%20invited%20both%20harsh%20criticism%20and%20voices%20of%20agreement.%20While%20some%20prominent%20business%20leaders%20backed%20Mr%20Muthy's%20workweek%20schedule%2C%20others%20on%20the%20internet%20slammed%20the%20billionaire%20and%20called%20his%20proposed%20work%20schedule%20inhumane.%20Now%2C%20actor%20and%20businessman%20Suniel%20Shetty%20has%20also%20shared%20his%20two%20cents%20on%20the%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20LinkedIn%20Post%2C%20Mr%20Shetty%20said%20that%20the%20way%20he%20sees%20things%20when%20someone%20like%20Mr%20Murthy%20says%20something%20people%20should%20listen%20carefully%2C%20analyse%20it%20for%20themselves%2C%20and%20take%20the%20best%20out%20of%20it.%20%26quot%3BEven%20though%20this%20is%20a%20contentious%20issue%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20stop%20%26amp%3B%20think%20about%20what%20he%20really%20meant.%20For%20me%2C%20it%20really%20isn't%20about%20the%20number%20of%20hours.%20It%20isn't%20about%2070%20or%20100%20hour%20weeks.%20The%20way%20I%20read%20his%20thoughts%20is%20simple%20-%20It's%20about%20going%20beyond%20your%20comfort%20zone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7125038777625976833%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221525%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20Mr%20Shetty%20cited%20examples%20of%20Abdul%20Kalam%2C%20Ratan%20Tata%2C%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20as%20individuals%20who%20excelled%20in%20their%20respective%20fields.%20%26quot%3BDo%20we%20really%20think%20any%20of%20these%20individuals%20got%20to%20where%20they%20did%20in%20life%2C%20by%20playing%20within%20their%20comfort%20zones%3F%20Do%20we%20really%20think%20any%20of%20these%20individuals%20spent%20the%20early%20years%20of%20their%20careers%20worrying%20about%20whether%20they%20were%20striking%20the%20right%20balance%20between%20work%20%26amp%3B%20life%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20backed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwonder-why-young-people-getting-heart-attacks-doctor-on-narayana-murthys-70-hour-workweek-suggestion-4523244%5C%22%3EMr%20Murthy's%2070-hour%20workweek%20schedule%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20I%20see%20Mr%20Murthy's%20statement%20for%20what%20it%20was%20really%20trying%20to%20convey%2C%20is%20because%20I%20do%20believe%20that%20young%20adults%20should%20spend%20their%20earliest%20years%20pushing%20their%20boundaries%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20highlighted%20that%20honing%20skills%2C%20acquiring%20new%20ones%2C%20dealing%20with%20pressure%2C%20learning%20about%20other%20functions%2C%20working%20in%20collaborative%20environments%20and%20generally%20making%20the%20most%20of%20the%20opportunities%2C%20should%20be%20top%20priorities%20for%20all%20young%20adults.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwonder-why-young-people-getting-heart-attacks-doctor-on-narayana-murthys-70-hour-workweek-suggestion-4523244%5C%22%3EWhy%20Young%20People%20Get%20Heart%20Attacks%3A%20Doctor%20On%20Narayana%20Murthy's%2070-Hour%20Workweek%20Suggestion%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Shetty%20concluded%20by%20saying%20that%20while%20it%20is%20important%20to%20have%20time%20for%20family%2C%20health%2C%20hobbies%2C%20friends%20as%20well%20as%20other%20things%2C%20it%20is%20also%20true%20that%20the%20world%20is%20evolving%20rapidly.%20%26quot%3BTechnology%20and%20AI%20are%20reshaping%20the%20world%20more%20than%20we%20can%20imagine.%20And%20we%20need%20to%20keep%20getting%20better.%20My%20dear%20future%20leaders%20-%20thrive%20for%20excellence%2C%20put%20in%20the%20hard%20work%20and%20cultivate%20your%20skills.%20Find%20mentors%2C%20build%20networks%20and%20invest%20in%20soft%20skills.%20The%20rest%20will%20fall%20into%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-suggests-70-hour-work-week-to-youngsters-sparks-debate-4516739%5C%22%3ENarayana%20Murthy%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecommented%20about%20the%20work%20culture%20while%20speaking%20to%20former%20Infosys%20CEO%20Mohandas%20Pai%20on%20the%20first%20episode%20of%203one4%20Capital's%20podcast%20'The%20Record'.%20He%20drew%20parallels%20to%20Japan%20and%20Germany%2C%20countries%20that%20implemented%20the%20extended%20working%20hours.%20He%20also%20talked%20about%20other%20topics%20like%20nation-building%2C%20technology%2C%20his%20company%20Infosys%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698859500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fmr4pb9q_suniel-shetty_625x300_11_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fthe-way-i-see-things-suniel-shetty-on-70-hour-workweek-suggestion-4536687%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Suniel%20Shetty%20backed%20Mr%20Murthy's%2070-hour%20workweek%20schedule%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20I%20see%20Mr%20Murthy's%20statement%20for%20what%20it%20was%20really%20trying%20to%20convey%2C%20is%20because%20I%20do%20believe%20that%20young%20adults%20should%20spend%20their%20earliest%20years%20pushing%20their%20boundaries%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fthe-way-i-see-things-suniel-shetty-on-70-hour-workweek-suggestion-4536687%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fthe-way-i-see-things-suniel-shetty-on-70-hour-workweek-suggestion-4536687%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fthe-way-i-see-things-suniel-shetty-on-70-hour-workweek-suggestion-4536687%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Another%20MiG-21%20Squadron%20Retired%3A%20The%20Curtain%20Is%20Closing%20on%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20Most%20Abiding%20Fighter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01222226%2FA_four_aircraft_Box_Formation_flown_by_Mig-21_FL_during_a_rehearsal_ahead_of_the_phasing-out_of_the_iconic_fighter_jets.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20has%20retired%20one%20of%20its%20three%20remaining%20Soviet-origin%20MiG-21%20%E2%80%98Bison%E2%80%99%20variant%20combat%20aircraft%20squadrons%20of%20around%2020%20platforms%2C%20and%20is%20committed%20to%20entirely%20phasing%20out%20this%20doughty%20fighter-type%20over%20the%20next%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20single-engine%2C%20single-seat%20MiG-21s%20that%20joined%20IAF%20service%20in%201963%20will%20be%20replaced%20gradually%20by%20the%20indigenous%20Mk1A%20advanced%20Tejas%20Light%20Combat%20t%20(LCA)%20model%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIAF%20spokesperson%20Wing%20Commander%20Asish%20Moghe%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20retiring%20MiG-21%20%E2%80%98Bis%E2%80%99%20fighters%2C%20which%20were%20being%20operated%20by%20No%204%20%E2%80%98Oorials%E2%80%99%20Squadron%20at%20Uttarlai%20near%20the%20Pakistan%20border%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20had%20been%20replaced%20by%20the%20more%20advanced%20Russian%20Sukhoi%20Su-30MKI%20(India)%20fighters.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20IAF%20aimed%20at%20retiring%20the%20remaining%20two%20MiG-21%20%E2%80%98Bis%E2%80%99%20squadrons%20%E2%80%93%20together%20comprising%20an%20estimated%2040%20fighters%20%E2%80%93%20based%20at%20nearby%20Bikaner%20and%20Suratgarh%2C%20by%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20IAF%20had%20%E2%80%98number%20plated%E2%80%99%20No%2050%20%E2%80%98Sword%20Arms%E2%80%9D%20Squadron%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20which%20also%20operated%20MiG-21s%2C%20reducing%20the%20fighter%20unit%20to%20just%20a%20number%20on%20paper%2C%20posting%20out%20all%20its%20personnel%20and%20re-distributing%20its%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20phasing%20out%20of%20the%20MiG-21s%20two%20years%20hence%20would%20bring%20down%20the%20curtain%20on%20possibly%20the%20most%20abiding%20fighter%20ever%20operated%20by%20the%20IAF%2C%20beginning%20with%20the%20MiG-211FL.%20A%20total%20of%20some%20870-odd%20MiG-21%20variants%20entered%20IAF%20service%20from%201963%20onwards%2C%20with%20the%20majority%20of%20them%20being%20licence-built%20by%20the%20public%20sector%20Hindustan%20Aeronautics%20Limited%20(HAL)%20in%20Bangalore.%20These%20continued%20to%20be%20inducted%20into%20squadron%20service%20till%20the%20mid-1980s.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20over%20decades%2C%20some%20500%20MiG-21s%20had%20crashed%2C%20killing%20around%20170-200%20pilots%20and%20many%20others%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20according%20to%20official%20statistics%20and%20led%20to%20the%20fighters%20being%20ignominiously%20dubbed%20by%20the%20media%20as%20%E2%80%98flying%20coffins%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98widowmakers%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20compulsion%20constrained%20the%20IAF%20to%20continue%20operating%20MiG-21s%20despite%20these%20mishaps.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20principal%20factor%20was%20the%20incessant%20delays%20in%20progressing%20the%20indigenous%20Light%20Combat%20Aircraft%20(LCA)%20programme%2C%20which%20began%20in%201983%2C%20primarily%20as%20a%20replacement%20option%20for%20the%20MiG-21.%20This%20compelled%20the%20IAF%20to%20keep%20the%20latter%20in%20service%20well%20beyond%20its%20use%20by%20date%20by%20resorting%20to%20%3Cem%3Ejugaad%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20creative%20innovation%2C%20for%20which%20the%20Indian%20military%20is%20deservedly%20lauded.%20And%2C%20in%20the%20late%201990s%2C%20the%20IAF%20opted%20to%20upgrade%20some%20125%20MiG-21%20%E2%80%98Bis%E2%80%99%20with%20Russian%20assistance%20to%20MiG-21%20%E2%80%98Bison%E2%80%99%20levels%20with%20locally%20developed%2C%20Russian%2C%20French%20and%20Israeli%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20though%20the%20fighter%E2%80%99s%20R-25%20engines%20were%20not%20replaced%2C%20they%20were%20%E2%80%98modified%E2%80%99%20with%20%E2%80%98enhanced%E2%80%99%20ancillary%20systems%20and%20accessory%20drives%20to%20power%20the%20heavier%20retrofitted%20fighters.%20The%20aircraft%E2%80%99s%20avionics%20were%20enhanced%20by%20fitting%20the%20platform%20with%20a%20lightweight%20Russian%20Super%20Kopyo%20multi-mode%20radar%20and%20a%20Totem%20221%20G%20ring-laser%20gyro%20inertial%20navigation%20system%20supplied%20by%20Sextant%20of%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20were%20merged%20with%20a%20locally%20developed%20navigation%20and%20attack%20computer%2C%20with%20the%20weapon%20solution%20displayed%20to%20the%20pilot%20in%20a%20heads-up%20display%20(HUD).%20The%20upgrade%20package%20also%20equipped%20the%20fighters%20with%20EWS-21%20radar%20warning%20receivers%20from%20Thales%20of%20France%2C%20Israeli%20flare%20dispensing%20systems%2C%20video%20recording%20systems%20and%20locally%20developed%20electronic%20countermeasures%20(ECMs).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20though%20the%20fighter%E2%80%99s%20endurance%20and%20payload%20restrictions%20remained%20the%20same%20as%20earlier%2C%20it%20now%20deployed%20a%20wider%20and%20varied%20range%20of%20ordnance%20like%20the%20Russian%20R-73%20and%20R-77%20air-to-air%20missiles%20with%20ranges%20between%2040-100%20km%20and%20Kh-31%20medium-range%20air-to-surface%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IAF%20scrambled%20four%20such%20MiG-21%20%E2%80%98Bis%E2%80%99%20in%20February%202019%20over%20Kashmir%20in%20response%20to%20the%20Pakistan%20Air%20Force%20attack%20over%20the%20disputed%20region%2C%20a%20day%20after%20Indian%20combat%20aircraft%20had%20bombed%20an%20alleged%20terrorist%20training%20camp%20at%20Balakaot%20in%20Pakistani%E2%80%99s%20north-western%20Pakhtunkhwa%20province.%20In%20the%20dogfight%20that%20ensued%20between%20the%20two%20air%20forces%2C%20IAF%20Wing%20Commander%20Abhinandan%20Varthaman%E2%80%99s%20MiG-21%20was%20shot%20down.%20But%20he%20bailed%20out%20safely%2C%20was%20taken%20captive%20by%20the%20Pakistanis%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Ffrom-close-quarters-how-abhinandan-varthaman-survived-across-the-loc%5C%22%3Ereturned%20home%20soon%20after%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20has%20now%20been%20promoted%20to%20a%20group%20captain%20rank.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%202013%2C%20delays%20by%20the%20MoD%20in%20clinching%20the%20long-pending%20procurement%20of%20126%20Dassault%20Rafale%20fighters%20%E2%80%93%20later%20scrapped%20in%202015%20%E2%80%93%20compelled%20the%20IAF%20to%20extend%20the%20operational%20life%20of%20several%20of%20its%20ageing%20platforms%2C%20including%20MiG-21%20%E2%80%98Bis%E2%80%99%2C%20beyond%20their%20retirement%20date%2C%20to%20keep%20them%20operational%20till%202023-25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20well%20beyond%20the%20MiG-21s%20phasing%20out%20deadline%20of%202019%2C%20announced%20by%20then%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20N.A.K.%20Browne%20in%20April%202013%2C%20with%20a%20view%20to%20maintaining%20the%20force%E2%80%99s%20rapidly%20depleting%20force%20levels%20at%2032-34%20fighter%20squadrons.%20Veteran%20officers%20said%20that%20at%20the%20time%20the%20IAF%20was%20left%20with%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20extend%20the%20service%20life%20of%20its%20older%20fighters%20like%20MiG-21s%20(and%20MiG-27s)%2C%20as%20there%20were%20no%20immediate%20alternatives%20available%20on%20the%20horizon.%20The%20IAF%2C%20said%20a%20former%20three-star%20fighter%20pilot%2C%20the%20force%20needed%20these%20MiG-21s%20to%20maintain%20%E2%80%98numerical%E2%80%99%20platform%20parity%20with%20the%20Pakistan%20Air%20Force%20and%20also%20with%20China%E2%80%99s%20People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Army%20Air%20Force.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Wing%20Commander%20(Retired)%20Amit%20Ranjan%20Giri%2C%20a%20veteran%20MIG-21%20pilot%2C%20is%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20fighter%20needed%20retiring%20as%20it%20was%20old%2C%20original%20equipment%20manufacturers%E2%80%99%20support%20was%20%E2%80%98drying%20up%E2%80%99%20and%2C%20above%20all%2C%20the%20technology%20it%20employed%20had%20been%20%E2%80%98superseded%E2%80%99.%20Writing%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Fbusiness%2Fdefence-the-mig-21-a-pilots-pov-should-she-go-or-stay-2390995%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20late%202021%2C%20he%20declared%20that%20though%20designed%20as%20a%20short-range%20interceptor%2C%20the%20IAF%20had%20%E2%80%9Cupped%20the%20game%20by%20using%20the%20MiG-21%20in%20almost%20every%20role%20imaginable%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20had%20included%20bombing%2C%20interception%2C%20reconnaissance%2C%20providing%20escort%20to%20bombers%20over%20enemy%20territory%20and%20training%20rookie%20pilots.%20The%20MiG-21%20had%20even%20comprised%20part%20of%20large%20force%20engagements%20(LFEs)%2C%20executed%20to%20deceive%20the%20enemy%20and%20conceal%20the%20real%20intent%20regarding%20intended%20targets%2C%20thereby%20forcing%20the%20opposing%20side%20to%20deploy%20a%20large%20defending%20package%20to%20its%20operational%20disadvantage.%20%E2%80%9CLet%20alone%20Western%20air%20forces%2C%20even%20the%20Russians%20could%20never%20have%20imagined%20the%20role%20of%20a%20MiG-21%20in%20LFE%E2%80%9D%20Wing%20Commander%20Giri%20said%20in%20a%20silent%20tribute%20to%20the%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20jugaad%20in%20optimising%20its%20assets%20for%20its%20novel%20war-fighting%20manoeuvres.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%