20Tickets%20Roils%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20facing%20a%20fresh%20hurdle%20in%20its%20quest%20to%20buck%20the%20'revolving%20door'%20trend%20in%20Rajasthan%20by%20winning%20a%20second%20straight%20term%20in%20the%20state.%20After%20the%20fourth%20and%20fifth%20lists%20for%20the%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20which%20will%20be%20held%20on%20November%2025%2C%20were%20released%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20infighting%20in%20the%20party%20has%20come%20to%20the%20fore%20in%20the%20form%20of%20protests%20by%20Congress%20workers%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20state.%20The%20workers%20are%20unhappy%20about%20their%20chosen%20leaders%20being%20denied%20tickets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20protests%20are%20emerging%20as%20a%20major%20headache%20for%20the%20Congress'%20central%20leadership%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20who%20has%20said%20that%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20keep%20everyone%20happy%2C%20but%20added%20that%20those%20who%20have%20been%20denied%20tickets%20may%20be%20accommodated%20in%20various%20boards.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20declared%20names%20for%20156%20of%20the%20200%20Assembly%20seats%20so%20far%20and%20three%20sticking%20points%20that%20have%20emerged%20are%20ministers%20Shanti%20Dhariwal%20and%20Mahesh%20Joshi%20and%20party%20leader%20Dharmendra%20Rathore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20had%20been%20issued%20a%20show-cause%20notice%20by%20the%20central%20leadership%20for%20their%20alleged%20rebellion%20ahead%20of%20the%20party's%20presidential%20elections%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20had%20emerged%20as%20one%20of%20the%20main%20contenders%20for%20the%20party%20president's%20post%20and%20it%20was%20later%20said%20that%20he%20would%20have%20to%20give%20up%20the%20chief%20ministership%20of%20Rajasthan%20under%20the%20'one%20man-one%20post%20principle'%2C%20at%20least%2072%20MLAs%20close%20to%20him%20had%20submitted%20their%20resignations%20to%20the%20Assembly%20speaker.%20The%20MLAs%20were%20opposed%20to%20Sachin%20Pilot%20being%20named%20the%20next%20chief%20minister%20and%20had%20cited%20his%202020%20rebellion%20against%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETicket%20Chances%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20protest%20at%20the%20party's%20headquarters%20in%20Jaipur%20on%20Wednesday%20was%20over%20the%20ticket%20to%20Mahesh%20Joshi%2C%20who%20is%20the%20sitting%20MLA%20for%20the%20Hawamahal%20constituency%2C%20the%20candidate%20for%20which%20has%20not%20even%20been%20declared%20yet.%20With%20Mr%20Joshi%20getting%20the%20high%20command's%20notice%20over%20the%20rebellion%20and%20his%20son%20facing%20a%20rape%20charge%2C%20there%20are%20strong%20indications%20that%20the%20ticket%20may%20go%20to%20the%20party's%20Jaipur%20unit%20president%20RR%20Tiwari.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhariwal%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20Mr%20Gehlot%20and%20the%20rebel%20MLAs%20had%20held%20a%20meeting%20at%20his%20residence%20instead%20of%20attending%20the%20Congress%20Legislature%20Party%20meet%20on%20September%2025%2C%202022.%20Mr%20Dhariwal%20had%20also%20allegedly%20said%20that%20Mr%20Gehlot%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Breal%20high%20command%26quot%3B.%20At%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20Congress%20Central%20Election%20Committee%20last%20month%2C%20former%20party%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20had%20allegedly%20objected%20to%20his%20name%20being%20part%20of%20the%20list%20of%20probables%20and%20had%20reportedly%20asked%20whether%20those%20who%20work%20against%20the%20party%20could%20feature%20in%20such%20a%20list.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESources%20have%20told%20NDTV%2C%20however%2C%20that%20there%20is%20a%20high%20probability%20of%20Mr%20Dhariwal%20being%20given%20a%20ticket%20to%20avoid%20antagonising%20the%20chief%20minister.%20But%20there%20is%20no%20clarity%20on%20whether%20Dharmendra%20Rathore%20will%20get%20to%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Structural%20Issues'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20played%20safe%20so%20far%20but%20the%20protests%20have%20begun%20after%20names%20were%20announced%20for%20some%20contested%20seats%20on%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20political%20strategist%20Amitabh%20Tiwari%20said%20that%20while%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20are%20facing%20problems%20with%20ticket%20distribution%2C%20the%20issue%20is%20bigger%20for%20the%20Congress%20because%20it%20has%20not%20managed%20to%20get%20a%20simple%20majority%20of%20101%20both%20times%20it%20formed%20the%20government%20in%20the%20last%20three%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20faces%20structural%20issues%20in%20Rajasthan...%20There%20are%2054%20seats%20it%20has%20never%20won%20in%20the%20last%20three%20elections.%20They%20need%20to%20win%20101%20of%20146%20seats%20to%20actually%20form%20the%20government%20and%20that%20is%20why%20they%20are%20falling%20short%20-%20sometimes%2096%20(seats)%2C%20sometimes%2099.%20And%20when%20they%20lose%2C%20they%20lose%20big%20because%20their%20stronghold%20seats%20are%20very%20less.%20So%20rebellion%20is%20a%20big%20problem%20for%20the%20Congress%20compared%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20never%20won%20only%20in%2019%20constituencies%20in%20the%20same%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20Factors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20shadow%20of%20the%20Sachin%20Pilot-Ashok%20Gehlot%20feud%2C%20which%20seems%20to%20have%20simmered%20down%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20elections%2C%20also%20hangs%20over%20the%20Congress%2C%20but%20what%20works%20in%20the%20party's%20favour%20is%20Mr%20Gehlot's%20clout%20and%20sound%20political%20instincts.%20He%20had%20managed%20to%20win%20over%20the%20support%20of%2012%20independents%20in%202018%20and%20they%20have%20been%20given%20Congress%20tickets%20this%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Pilot%20has%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20he%20will%20decide%20who%20will%20be%20chief%20minister%20once%20the%20party%20wins%2C%20indicating%20that%20he%20has%20also%20been%20promised%20something.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Tiwari%20said%20the%20BJP%20finds%20it%20easier%20to%20drop%20sitting%20MLAs%20and%20even%20replace%20members%20of%20the%20cabinet%20like%20they%20had%20done%20in%20Gujarat%20because%20it%20is%20a%20cadre-based%20party%20aligned%20to%20an%20ideology.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20Congress%2C%20however%2C%20the%20cadre%20in%20any%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20seat%20is%20split%20between%20the%20top%20four%20to%20five%20leaders.%20So%20when%20one%20person%20gets%20the%20ticket%2C%20the%20cadre%20loyal%20to%20the%20other%20leaders%20goes%20silent%20and%20does%20not%2C%20normally%2C%20work%20for%20the%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Tiwari%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20seeing%20issues%20in%20the%20Rajasthan%20BJP%20as%20well%2C%20but%20once%20a%20candidate%20is%20announced%2C%20the%20ideology%20ensures%20that%20a%20relatively%20larger%20number%20of%20workers%20back%20him%20or%20her.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20protests%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20said%20that%20it%20is%20not%20surprising%20that%20a%20party%20in%20power%20is%20seeing%20more%20instances%20of%20candidates%20wanting%20a%20ticket%20and%20being%20unhappy%20when%20it%20is%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTickets%20are%20decided%20based%20on%20a%20process%2C%20based%20on%20surveys%20and%20consultations%2C%20and%20that%20takes%20time.%20It%20should%20take%20time.%20It%20is%20natural%20for%20some%20people%20to%20be%20disappointed.%20We%20are%20the%20winning%20party%2C%20just%20look%20at%20how%20much%20fighting%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20losing%20party.%20It%20is%20natural%20for%20there%20to%20be%20some%20anger%20in%20the%20winning%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Pawan%20Khera.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698856860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-1