0%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-reservation-without-touching-existing-quotas-eknath-shinde-4534809%5C%22%3Ewho%20chaired%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20today%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20discuss%20the%20fresh%20wave%20of%20statewide%20protests%2C%20said%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20is%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Maratha%20quota.%20Mr%20Shinde%20said%20that%20reservation%20should%20be%20given%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community%20without%20tampering%20with%20the%20existing%20quotas%20of%20other%20communities%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20which%20was%20attended%20by%20NCP%20veteran%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Ashok%20Chavan%20among%20others%20passed%20a%20unanimous%20resolution%20to%20improve%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20Maratha%20reservations%20is%20not%20new%20and%20the%20push%20for%20it%20has%20been%20going%20on%20for%20four%20decades.%20Here%2C%20we%20chart%20the%20Maratha%20quota%20issue%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20Did%20the%20Maratha%20Quota%20Protests%20Start%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EMarathas%2C%20who%20constitute%20nearly%2033%25%20of%20the%20state's%20population%2C%20have%20been%20demanding%20the%20reservation%20in%20education%20and%20government%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%20the%20year%201981%20when%20the%20state%20saw%20its%20first%20protests%20demanding%20the%20Maratha%20reservation%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20Mathadi%20Labour%20Union%20leader%20Annasaheb%20Patil.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20community%20has%20been%20seeking%20Kunbi%20caste%20certificates%20for%20Marathas%20which%20will%20enable%20their%20inclusion%20in%20the%20OBC%20category%20for%20reservation.%20Kunbis%2C%20who%20are%20associated%20with%20agriculture%2C%20are%20grouped%20under%20the%20OBC%20(Other%20Backward%20Classes)%20cat