20framework%20to%20assess%20the%20on-ground%20implementation%20of%20these%20schemes%20and%20hold%20accountable%20all%20defaulters%20whose%20aim%20is%20solely%20to%20forge%20numbers.%20We%20discuss%20more%20on%20this%20in%20part%202%20of%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDeepanshu%20Mohan%20is%20professor%20of%20economics%20and%20director%2C%20CNES.%20Amisha%20Singh%20and%20Aditi%20Desai%20are%20research%20assistants%20with%20CNES%20and%20co-leads%20of%20the%20InfoSphere%20team.%20Vasudevan%2C%20Shilpa%20Santhosh%2C%20Aryan%20Govindakrishnan%20and%20Jheel%20Doshi%20are%20members%20of%20the%20InfoSphere%20team%20and%20research%20assistants%20with%20CNES.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698853832000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-government-underperform-developing-rural-economy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rural%20income%20is%20a%20key%20driver%20of%20rural%20demand%2C%20which%20has%20ripple%20effects%20on%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20industries%2C%20including%20fast-moving%20consumer%20goods.%20Figures%20show%20that%20rural%20job%20demand%20has%20not%20been%20met.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dancing%20Queen!%20Camilla%20in%20Kenya%20animal%20sanctuary%20visit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698852803000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F7D09%2Fproduction%2F_131590023_p0gq5j1x.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-67289523%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Queen%20joined%20a%20traditional%20dance%20in%20Nairobi%20and%20stopped%20to%20feed%20orphaned%20elephants.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fuk-67289523%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Phase%20Out%20Fossil%20Fuels%20for%20Healthy%20World%3A%2046%20Million%20Healthcare%20Professionals%20Write%20to%20COP28%20Presidency%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01203806%2Fpexels-marcin-jozwiak-3641377.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EKochi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20More%20than%2046%20million%20healthcare%20professionals%20from%20around%20the%20world%20on%20November%201%20endorsed%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcop28healthletter.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eletter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20addressed%20to%20the%20president-designate%20of%20the%2028th%20Conference%20of%20Parties%20(COP28)%2C%20calling%20on%20leaders%20of%20all%20countries%20to%20commit%20to%20%E2%80%9Caccelerating%20the%20phase-out%E2%80%9D%20of%20fossil%20fuels%20%E2%80%93%20in%20a%20just%20and%20equitable%20way%20%E2%80%93%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20decisive%20path%20to%20health%20for%20all%E2%80%9D.%20The%20letter%20cites%20the%20impacts%20on%20human%20health%20due%20to%20the%20extreme%20weather%20caused%20by%20climate%20change%20and%20the%20millions%20of%20premature%20deaths%20that%20air%20pollution%20causes%20worldwide%20annually%20%E2%80%93%20both%20caused%20largely%20by%20fossil%20fuel%20combustion%20%E2%80%93%20as%20reasons%20for%20the%20phase-out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20annual%20UN%20conference%20on%20climate%20change%2C%20leaders%20and%20governments%20will%20discuss%20several%20aspects%20of%20climate%20change%20such%20as%20the%20means%20to%20curb%20and%20deal%20with%20the%20impacts%20of%20ongoing%20global%20warming%20by%20methods%20including%20decreasing%20the%20use%20of%20polluting%20fossil%20fuels.%20It%20will%20be%20underway%20from%20November%2030%20to%20December%2012%20in%20Dubai%2C%20UAE.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFull%20and%20rapid%20phase-out%20of%20fossil%20fuels%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20year%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20COPs%2C%20health%20is%20on%20the%20agenda.%20One%20day%2C%20December%203%2C%20will%20be%20dedicated%20to%20discussions%20on%20health%20alone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20than%2046%20million%20healthcare%20professionals%20%E2%80%93%20including%20those%20affiliated%20with%20the%20World%20Medical%20Association%2C%20World%20Federation%20of%20Public%20Health%20Association%20and%20International%20Council%20of%20Nurses%20%E2%80%93%20have%20endorsed%20a%20letter%20addressed%20to%20president-designate%20Sultan%20Ahmed%20Al-Jaber%2C%20supporting%20this%20move%20to%20bring%20health%20%E2%80%9Cfront%20and%20centre%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20keeping%20the%20global%20temperature%20increase%20within%20the%201.5%C2%B0C%20target%20of%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%20will%20happen%20only%20if%20we%20rapidly%20phase%20out%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20the%20letter%20noted.%20Failure%20to%20do%20so%20can%20%E2%80%9Clead%20to%20overwhelming%20health%20consequences%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20warned.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20call%20on%20the%20COP28%20Presidency%20and%20the%20leaders%20of%20all%20countries%20to%20commit%20to%20an%20accelerated%2C%20just%20and%20equitable%20phase-out%20of%20fossil%20fuels%20as%20the%20decisive%20path%20to%20health%20for%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcop28healthletter.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eletter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20coordinated%20by%20international%20NGOs%20Health%20Care%20Without%20Harm%20and%20Global%20Climate%20and%20Health%20Alliance%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20health%20community%2C%20read.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20because%20combustion%20of%20fossil%20fuels%20adds%20to%20carbon%20emissions%20that%20accelerate%20global%20warming%20and%20cause%20climate%20change.%20The%20latter%20also%20manifests%20in%20extreme%20weather%20events%20such%20as%20intense%20heat%20waves%20that%20are%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20health%20of%20both%20human%20and%20non-human%20species.%20Fossil%20fuel%20use%20also%20releases%20pollutants%20into%20the%20air%2C%20and%20these%20are%20known%20to%20cause%20direct%20impacts%20on%20human%20health.%20One%20of%20the%20pollutants%20is%20particulate%20matter%20(PM%2C%20or%20solid%20inhalable%20particles%20ranging%20from%20fine%20diameters%20of%202.5%20mm%20to%20larger%20ones%20of%2010%20mm)%20and%20these%20are%20known%20to%20cause%20public%20health%20issues%20ranging%20from%20respiratory%20illnesses%20to%20cancers.%20According%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fwesternpacific%2Fhealth-topics%2Fair-pollution%23tab%3Dtab_1%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWorld%20Health%20Organisation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20air%20pollution%20%E2%80%93%20which%20fossil%20fuels%20and%20other%20pollutants%20contribute%20%E2%80%93%20causes%207%20million%20premature%20deaths%20annually.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20full%20and%20rapid%20phase-out%20of%20fossil%20fuels%20is%20the%20most%20significant%20way%20to%20provide%20the%20clean%20air%2C%20water%2C%20and%20environment%20that%20are%20foundational%20to%20good%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20solutions%20such%20as%20Carbon%20Capture%20and%20Storage%20%E2%80%93%20put%20forward%20by%20the%20oil%20industry%20%E2%80%93%20are%20%E2%80%9Cunreliable%20and%20inadequate%E2%80%9D.%20Per%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iea.org%2Fenergy-system%2Fcarbon-capture-utilisation-and-storage%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EInternational%20Energy%20Agency%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20CCS%20techniques%20involve%20capturing%20carbon%20dioxide%20from%20fossil%20fuel-based%20sources%20like%20power%20generation%20or%20industrial%20facilities%20and%20burying%20them%20in%20%E2%80%9Cdeep%20geological%20formations%20such%20as%20depleted%20oil%20and%20gas%20reservoirs%20or%20saline%20aquifers%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20letter%20demands%20that%20energy%20transition%20be%20made%20just%20and%20equitable%20for%20all%2C%20and%20that%20unlocking%20finance%20will%20be%20crucial%20for%20this.%20It%20also%20highlighted%20that%20%E2%80%9Cfossil%20fuel%20interests%20have%20no%20place%20at%20climate%20negotiations%E2%80%9D.%20In%20January%20this%20year%2C%20the%20UAE%20announced%20that%20Al-Jaber%2C%20the%20UAE%E2%80%99s%20minister%20of%20industry%20and%20advanced%20technology%2C%20would%20be%20president-designate.%20Al-Jaber%2C%20however%2C%20is%20also%20the%20serving%20CEO%20of%20the%20UAE-owned%20Abu%20Dhabi%20National%20Oil%20Company%20(ADNOC)%2C%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fuae-oil-company-adnoc-ceo-cop28-president%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20January.%20Activists%20worldwide%20expressed%20concern%20at%20the%20move%2C%20calling%20the%20appointment%20%E2%80%9Coutrageously%20regressive%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20problematic%E2%80%9D%2C%20among%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20representatives%20of%20the%20global%20medical%20community%2C%20we%20fully%20support%20this%20letter%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dr%20Lujain%20Alqodmani%2C%20president%20of%20the%20World%20Medical%20Association%2C%20in%20a%20press%20release.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20already%20seeing%20the%20impacts%20of%20the%20climate%20crisis%20on%20our%20health%20%E2%80%93%20heat%20stress%2C%20malnutrition%2C%20anxiety%2C%20vector-borne%20diseases%2C%20respiratory%20illnesses%20due%20to%20dirty%20air%20to%20name%20a%20few.%20Extreme%20weather%20events%20have%20another%20far%20reaching%20impact-%20hospitals%20and%20healthcare%20centres%20that%20are%20meant%20to%20provide%20cure%20and%20relief%20are%20often%20first%20in%20the%20line%20of%20fire%2C%20with%20access%20and%20infrastructure%20getting%20hit.%20Our%20dangerous%20addiction%20to%20fossil%20fuels%20will%20only%20aggravate%20this%20further.%20This%20is%20why%20we%20think%20that%20a%20rapid%20transition%20to%20clean%20and%20equitable%20forms%20of%20energy%20is%20a%20win-win%20on%20all%20fronts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F13153457%2FFmVbkERWQAAN67n-e1673604693189.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F13153457%2FFmVbkERWQAAN67n-e1673604693189.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F13153457%2FFmVbkERWQAAN67n-e1673604693189-300x150.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F13153457%2FFmVbkERWQAAN67n-e1673604693189-1024x512.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F13153457%2FFmVbkERWQAAN67n-e1673604693189-800x400.jpeg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-636042%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESultan%20Ahmed%20Al%20Jaber.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40FC_actu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIndia%2C%20air%20pollution%20and%20child%20health%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20well-known%20fact%20that%20air%20pollution%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20indoor%20or%20outdoor%20%E2%80%93%20adversely%20affects%20children%20and%20we%20are%20seeing%20that%20in%20our%20practice%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Naveen%20Thacker%2C%20president%20of%20the%20International%20Pediatric%20Association%20and%20one%20of%20the%20signatories%20of%20the%20letter%2C%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDefinitely%20as%20a%20pediatrician%2C%20I%20see%20an%20increase%20of%20cases%20in%20respiratory%20illnesses%20such%20as%20asthma%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%20Thacker%20is%20also%20the%20director%20of%20Deep%20Children%20Hospital%20and%20Research%20Centre%20at%20Gandhigram%2C%20Kutch%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20former%20president%20of%20the%20Asia%20Pacific%20Pediatric%20Association%20and%20former%20national%20president%20of%20the%20Indian%20Academy%20of%20Pediatrics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS0048969721078347%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estudy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%202022%20by%20a%20team%20of%20scientists%20from%20across%20the%20world%2C%20including%20IIT%20Delhi%2C%20found%20a%20%E2%80%9Crobust%20relationship%E2%80%9D%20between%20ambient%20air%20pollution%20and%20infant%20mortality%20(death%20of%20children%20under%20five%20years%20of%20age)%20in%20India%20when%20they%20studied%20the%20data%20on%20particulate%20matter%20(PM2.5)%20from%20satellite%20imagery%2C%20and%20data%20from%20the%20Demographic%20and%20Health%20Survey%20of%20India%20of%202015-2016.%20They%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.iitd.ac.in%2F~sagnik%2FSTOTEN2022.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexamined%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20data%20pertaining%20to%20more%20than%202.5%20lakh%20children%20across%20640%20districts%20in%20India.%20Preliminary%20descriptive%20analyses%20showed%20that%20children%20who%20died%20in%20the%20first%20year%20of%20their%20lives%20were%20less%20privileged%20than%20those%20who%20survived%20(based%20on%20factors%20such%20as%20lower%20wealth%20quintile%20and%20less%20maternal%20education).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENorth%20India%20stands%20out%2C%20because%20pollution%20levels%20are%20higher%20in%20the%20area%2C%20per%20a%20separate%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brookings.edu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FEarly-life-Exposure-to-Outdoor-air-pollution.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epreliminary%20study%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%202019.%20Researchers%20affiliated%20with%20the%20Indian%20Statistical%20Institute%20Delhi%2C%20Brookings%20India%20and%20IIT%20Delhi%20(using%20similar%20methods%20as%20in%20the%202022%20study)%20found%20that%20air%20pollution%20negatively%20affects%20child%20health%20in%20India%20in%20their%20working%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brookings.edu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FEarly-life-Exposure-to-Outdoor-air-pollution.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epaper%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Exposure%20to%20air%20pollution%20during%20the%20first%20trimester%20of%20pregnancy%20decreases%20both%20height-for-age%20(a%20measure%20of%20stunting%2C%20when%20a%20child%20is%20too%20short%20for%20their%20age)%20and%20weight-for-age%20(a%20measure%20of%20being%20underweight)%20for%20children%20below%20five%20years%20of%20age.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20effect%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9Cis%20prominent%20for%20poorer%20households%2C%20with%20Northern%20states%20being%20more%20vulnerable%20due%20to%20high%20pollution%20levels%20in%20the%20area.%E2%80%9D%20Their%20study%20looked%20at%20not%20just%20child%20mortality%2C%20but%20also%20the%20growth%20indicators%20that%20play%20a%20role%20in%20child%20survival.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncreasing%20awareness%20of%20how%20to%20prevent%20or%20reduce%20exposure%20to%20air%20pollutants%20such%20as%20particulate%20matter%20is%20important%2C%20Thacker%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20These%20include%20gauging%20air%20pollution%20levels%20to%20use%20masks%20to%20reduce%20exposure%2C%20or%20small%20steps%20that%20can%20be%20practised%20at%20home%20to%20decrease%20indoor%20air%20pollution.%20Controlling%20the%20number%20of%20fires%20that%20some%20areas%20such%20as%20north%20India%20tend%20to%20witness%20during%20the%20winter%20months%20is%20also%20important%20and%20people%20should%20be%20made%20aware%20that%20this%20is%20a%20problem%2C%20added%20Thacker.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20Thacker%20spoke%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20November%201%2C%20particulate%20matter%20PM2.5%20and%20PM10%20dominated%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20air%2C%20and%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcpcb.nic.in%2F%2Fupload%2FDownloads%2FAQI_Bulletin_20231101.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAir%20Quality%20Index%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%204%20pm%20(averaged%20across%20the%20last%2024%20hours)%20was%20364%2C%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9CVery%20Poor%E2%80%9D%20category.%20Per%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%2C%20prolonged%20exposure%20to%20such%20air%20quality%20can%20cause%20respiratory%20illnesses.%20The%20national%20capital%20is%20notorious%20for%20poor%20and%20sometimes%20severe%20air%20quality%20during%20the%20winter%20months%20(November%20to%20January).%20While%20studies%20show%20that%20farm%20fires%20%E2%80%93%20stubble%20burning%20of%20crop%20residue%20in%20farms%20%E2%80%93%20across%20Delhi%20NCR%2C%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20are%20one%20of%20the%20major%20contributors%20to%20the%20worsening%20air%20quality%20in%20the%20city%20(and%20often%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fexplainer-delhis-air-quality-dips-but-only-weather-conditions-to-blame-yet%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaided%20by%20meteorological%20conditions%20such%20as%20low%20wind%20speed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E)%2C%20particulate%20matter%20released%20by%20industries%20and%20vehicular%20emissions%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubs.acs.org%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1021%2Facs.est.0c00329%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eare%20also%20part%20of%20the%20picture%20here%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20has%20pledged%20to%20decrease%20carbon%20emissions%20as%20per%20its%20submissions%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20as%20part%20of%20its%20Nationally%20Determined%20Contributions.%20However%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fexternal-affairs%2Fworld%2Fcop26-india-coal-phase-down-necessary-just-transition%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20government%20has%20made%20it%20clear%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20a%20complete%20phase-out%20of%20fossil%20fuels%20is%20impossible%20since%20India%E2%80%99s%20historical%20contributions%20to%20climate%20change%20have%20been%20minimal%20(even%20though%20India%20is%20the%20second-highest%20carbon%20emitter%20currently).%20India%20has%20argued%20for%20a%20phase-down%20of%20fossil%20fuels%20instead%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20energy%20transition%20to%20cleaner%20and%20greener%20forms%20such%20as%20solar%20and%20wind%20will%20not%20impact%20the%20people%20depending%20on%20the%20fossil%20fuel%20industry%20in%20the%20country%2C%20or%20impede%20India%E2%80%99s%20economic%20ambitions.%20Just%20and%20equitable%20transitioning%2C%20therefore%2C%20is%20crucial%20for%20developing%20countries%20that%20depend%20heavily%20on%20fossil%20fuels%20for%20growth%2C%20experts%20have%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fexternal-affairs%2Fworld%2Fcop26-india-coal-phase-down-necessary-just-transition%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eargued%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Thacker%2C%20India%20is%20making%20%E2%80%9Cgreat%20progress%E2%80%9D%2C%20through%20its%20current%20pledges.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20can%20commit%20more%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20good%20step%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20to%20always%20be%20a%20balance%20though%3A%20we%20cannot%20commit%20without%20ensuring%20proper%20rehabilitation%20to%20people%2C%20and%20that%20the%20process%20be%20just%20and%20equitable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698852023000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01203806%2Fpexels-marcin-jozwiak-3641377.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fphase-out-fossil-fuels-46-million-healthcare-professionals-cop28-presidency%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Keeping%20the%20global%20temperature%20increase%20within%20the%201.5%C2%B0C%20target%20of%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%20will%20happen%20only%20if%20we%20rapidly%20phase%20out%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20the%20letter%20notes%2C%20adding%20that%20failure%20to%20do%20so%20can%20%E2%80%9Clead%20to%20overwhelming%20health%20consequences%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fphase-out-fossil-fuels-46-million-healthcare-professionals-cop28-presidency%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHo%20Sakta%20Hai...%26quot%3B%3A%20Rohit's%201st%20Official%20Update%20On%20Pandya's%20WC%20Return%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20player%20who%20provides%20balance%20to%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20unlike%20any%20other%20player.%20Top%20class%20fast-bowling%20all-rounder%20is%20a%20rare%20commodity%20in%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya%20is%20one%20such%20player.%20He%20gave%20a%20good%20account%20of%20himself%20in%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20matches%20that%20he%20played%20before%20injury%20pushed%20him%20to%20the%20sidelines.%C2%A0Pandya%20had%20hurt%20his%20left%20ankle%20while%20fielding%20on%20his%20own%20bowling%20in%20the%20game%20against%20Bangladesh%20in%20Pune%20on%20October%2019.%20He%20missed%20the%20games%20against%20New%20Zealand%20and%20England%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndian%20cricket%20team%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20during%20the%20pre-match%20press%20conference%20ahead%20of%20the%20game%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20Thursday%2C%20said%20that%20Hardik%20Pandya%20will%20miss%20the%20game%20but%20had%20a%20godd%20news%20also.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVery%20positive%20development.%20I%20cant's%20call%20it%20rehab%20but%20whatever%20is%20the%20procedure%20that%20he%20and%20the%20NCA%20had%20to%20undertake%2C%20they%20have%20got%20positive%20results.%20He%20is%20not%20available%20for%20next%20match.%20The%20injury%20is%20such%20that%20we%20have%20to%20monitor%20it%20everyday.%20What%20is%20the%20percentage%20of%20recovery%2C%20we%20have%20to%20monitor%20his%20batting%20and%20bowling%20load.%20we%20are%20looking%20at%20World%20Cup%20where%20there%20are%20matches%20every%20three%20to%20four%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EHo%20Sakta%20Hai%2C%20Jaisa%20unka%20chal%20raha%20hai%2C%20jald%20se%20jald%20dekhneka%20mauka%20milega%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Maybe%2C%20the%20good%20progress%20that%20he%20is%20making.%20We%20will%20get%20to%20see%20him%20soon.)%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20star%20India%20all-rounder%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20who%20is%20recovering%20from%20an%20ankle%20injury%2C%20is%20unlikely%20to%20return%20to%20action%20before%20the%20team's%20World%20Cup%20match%20against%20the%20Netherlands%20on%20November%2012.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia's%20final%20league%20match%20is%20against%20Netherlands%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20November%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20minor%20tear.%20He%20is%20recovering%20well%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20return%20for%20the%20last%20league%20game.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20possibility%20that%20he%20straight%20away%20plays%20the%20semifinal%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20BCCI%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20six%20wins%20in%20as%20many%20games%2C%20India%20are%20set%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20semifinals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20compensate%20for%20Pandya's%20all-round%20abilities%2C%20the%20team%20was%20forced%20to%20make%20two%20changes%20to%20the%20playing%20eleven.%20In%20his%20absence%2C%20the%20management%20is%20playing%20with%20five%20bowlers%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Suryakumar%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1492-suryakumar-yadav-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESuryakumar%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20batting%20at%20six%20in%20his%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20medical%20team%20is%20looking%20at%20that%20and%20are%20very%20much%20in%20touch%20with%20Hardik%20and%20the%20NCA%20(National%20Cricket%20Academy)%20as%20well.%20We're%20hoping%20to%20get%20an%20update%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20Mhambrey%20had%20said%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20BCCI%20media%20release%2C%20Pandya%20was%20supposed%20to%20join%20the%20team%20in%20Lucknow%20ahead%20of%20the%20England%20game%20but%20he%20was%20not%20with%20the%20squad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698852000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F9h5rd6vs_hardik-pandya-ani_640x480_21_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fho-sakta-hai-rohit-sharmas-1st-big-official-update-on-hardik-pandyas-return-in-cricket-world-cup-4536216%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Top%20class%20fast-bowling%20all-rounder%20is%20a%20rare%20commodity%20in%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya%20is%20one%20such%20player%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fho-sakta-hai-rohit-sharmas-1st-big-official-update-on-hardik-pandyas-return-in-cricket-world-cup-4536216%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fho-sakta-hai-rohit-sharmas-1st-big-official-update-on-hardik-pandyas-return-in-cricket-world-cup-4536216%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fho-sakta-hai-rohit-sharmas-1st-big-official-update-on-hardik-pandyas-return-in-cricket-world-cup-4536216%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20To%20Buy%20Venezuelan%20Oil%3F%20What%20Minister%20Said%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20refiners%20can%20process%20Venezuelan%20oil%20and%20the%20nation%20may%20buy%20it%20provided%20that%20it%20is%20available%20cheaply%2C%20Oil%20Minister%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Puri%20said%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20days%20after%20the%20US%20temporarily%20lifted%20sanctions%20on%20OPEC%20member%20Venezuela's%20oil%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20the%20world's%20third%20biggest%20oil%20importer%20and%20consumer%20and%20ships%20over%2080%25%20of%20its%20oil%20needs%20from%20overseas%20and%20wants%20to%20cut%20its%20crude%20import%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20always%20good%20when%20more%20supplies%20come%20to%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Oil%20Minister%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Puri%20said%20at%20an%20industry%20event%2C%20speaking%20about%20Venezuelan%20oil%2C%20and%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20buy%20from%20wherever%20we%20can%20get%20cheaper%20oil.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVenezuela%20has%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20oil%20reserves%20and%20production%20from%20it%20at%20a%20large%20scale%20will%20have%20a%20dampening%20effect%20on%20global%20oil%20prices%2C%20Mr%20Puri%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20South%20American%20country%20had%20been%20under%20crushing%20sanctions%20since%202019.%20These%20were%20broadly%20lifted%20by%20the%20US%20two%20weeks%20ago%20in%20response%20to%20a%20deal%20reached%20between%20the%20Venezuelan%20government%20and%20opposition%20parties%20for%20the%202024%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20new%20general%20licence%20issued%20by%20the%20US%20Treasury%20Department%20authorises%20Venezuela%20to%20produce%20and%20export%20oil%20to%20its%20chosen%20markets%20for%20the%20next%20six%20months%20without%20limitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndian%20Oil%20Corp%20and%20Reliance%20Industries%20have%20bought%20Venezuelan%20oil%20in%20the%20past%2C%20Mr%20Puri%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698851820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-02%2Fbrku99rk_venezuelan-oil-reuters_625x300_18_February_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-buy-venezuelan-oil-what-minister-said-4536211%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20refiners%20can%20process%20Venezuelan%20oil%20and%20the%20nation%20may%20buy%20it%20provided%20that%20it%20is%20available%20cheaply%2C%20Oil%20Minister%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Puri%20said%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20days%20after%20the%20US%20temporarily%20lifted%20sanctions%20on%20OPEC%20member%20Venezuela's%20oil%20sector.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-buy-venezuelan-oil-what-minister-said-4536211%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%3A%20A%20Land%20of%20Settled%20Grief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F08131052%2FF7SQIIebEAAHp2K.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManipur%2C%20literally%20the%20%E2%80%98jewelled%20land%E2%80%99%2C%20today%20is%20the%20theatre%20of%20a%20full-blown%20civil%20war%20of%20the%20kind%20that%20free%20India%20has%20not%20seen.%20Civilian%20populations%20on%20both%20sides%20flaunt%20sophisticated%20modern%20weapons%20including%20assault%20rifles%2C%20light%20machine%20guns%20and%20mortars.%20Even%20five%20months%20after%20the%20conflagration%20began%2C%20the%20combat%20shows%20no%20sign%20of%20an%20end.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20rare%20for%20even%20a%20day%20to%20pass%20without%20the%20rattle%20of%20gunfire%20and%20bombs%20and%20news%20of%20fresh%20deaths%20and%20injuries.%20The%20state%20of%20Manipur%20is%20effectively%20partitioned%2C%20the%20valley%20emptied%20out%20of%20the%20last%20of%20its%20Kuki%20residents%2C%20as%20the%20Kuki%20dominated%20southern%20hills%20are%20of%20their%20Meitei%20inhabitants.%20The%20border%20between%20the%20valley%20and%20the%20Kuki%20dominated%20part%20of%20the%20hills%20%E2%80%93%20guarded%20and%20patrolled%20by%20military%20and%20paramilitary%20personnel%20of%20diverse%20stripes%20and%20uniforms%20%E2%80%93%20is%20mutually%20impenetrable%20for%20people%20of%20the%20two%20respective%20warring%20communities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%E2%80%99s%20groups%20successfully%20blockade%20for%20weeks%20the%20passage%20of%20army%20trucks%20carrying%20food%20supplies%20for%20soldiers%20in%20the%20hills.%20No%20rations%20have%20been%20supplied%20by%20the%20state%20government%20for%20patients%20and%20students%20in%20the%20medical%20college%20in%20the%20hills.%20Teachers%2C%20doctors%2C%20nurses%20and%20even%20police%20persons%20have%20been%20reallocated%20(or%20have%20fled)%20on%20ethnic%20lines%20to%20the%20two%20sides%20of%20this%20border%3A%20it%20is%20unsafe%20for%20Kuki%20public%20servants%20to%20work%20in%20the%20valley%2C%20as%20it%20is%20for%20Meitei%20public%20servants%20to%20work%20in%20the%20Kuki%20dominated%20part%20of%20the%20hills.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12101935%2FF3L9084aoAAReUs.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12101935%2FF3L9084aoAAReUs.jpeg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12101935%2FF3L9084aoAAReUs-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12101935%2FF3L9084aoAAReUs-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-672643%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image%20of%20Army%20Commander%20Lt%20Gen.%20R.P.%20Kalita%20interacting%20with%20Manipur%20CM%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20in%20August.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40easterncomd%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ten%20Kuki%20members%20of%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20were%20unable%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20record%20eleven-minute-long%20legislative%20assembly%20session%20because%20the%20government%20could%20not%20ensure%20their%20safety.These%20ten%20Kuki%20MLAs%2C%20including%20eight%20from%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20expressed%20their%20despair%20in%20a%20public%20statement%3A%20%E2%80%9COur%20people%20can%20no%20longer%20exist%20under%20Manipur%20as%20the%20hatred%20against%20our%20tribal%20community%20reached%20such%20a%20height%20that%20MLAs%2C%20ministers%2C%20pastors%2C%20police%20and%20civil%20officers%2C%20laymen%2C%20women%20and%20even%20children%20were%20not%20spared%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20destruction%20of%20places%20of%20worships%2C%20homes%20and%20properties.%E2%80%9D%20To%20live%20amid%20the%20Meiteis%20after%20the%20violence%2C%20they%20declared%2C%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1049014%2Fmanipur-violence-all-10-kuki-mlas-demand-separate-administration-for-their-community%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20good%20as%20death%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20anguish%20of%20a%20retired%20Lieutenant%20General%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20living%20in%20Manipur%20is%20even%20more%20palpable.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20state%20is%20now%20%E2%80%98stateless%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20laments%20Lt%20Gen%20Nishikanta%20Singh.%20%E2%80%9CLife%20and%20property%20can%20be%20destroyed%20anytime%20by%20anyone%20just%20like%20in%20Libya%2C%20Lebanon%2C%20Nigeria%2C%20Syria%2C%20etc.%E2%80%9D.%20This%20spurred%20a%20former%20chief%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20General%20Ved%20Malik%20to%20respond%2C%20%E2%80%9CLaw%20%26amp%3B%20order%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20needs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1051145%2Ffrom-mob-violence-to-manipur-the-past-decade-has-weakened-the-indian-state%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eurgent%20attention%20at%20%5Bthe%5D%20highest%20level%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManipur%20%E2%80%93%20an%20ethnic%20mosaic%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20current%20battle%20between%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20people%20centres%20on%20competing%20claims%20of%20indigeneity%2C%20belonging%20and%20non-belonging%3A%20about%20which%20people%20are%20indigenous%20to%20Manipur%2C%20and%20who%20are%20outsiders.%20There%20is%20no%20dispute%20that%20the%20Meitei%20people%20are%20native%20to%20the%20Manipur%20valley%2C%20and%20the%20Nagas%20to%20the%20hills.%20But%20the%20Kukis%20insist%20that%20they%20too%20have%20long%20been%20inhabitants%20of%20the%20Manipur%20hills%2C%20and%20are%20not%20%E2%80%9Cforeigners%E2%80%9D%20from%20Myanmar%20as%20is%20now%20claimed.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20three%20main%20ethnic%20groups%20in%20Manipur%20have%20historically%20clustered%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20geography%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Meiteis%20in%20the%20valley%2C%20the%20Kukis%20in%20the%20southern%20hills%20and%20the%20Nagas%20in%20the%20northern%20hills.%20But%20there%20has%20not%20been%2C%20before%20the%202023%20combat%2C%20an%20absolute%2C%20hostile%20segregation%20of%20the%20communities.%20In%20places%20dominated%20by%20one%20ethnic%20group%2C%20there%20have%20grown%20minority%20settlements%20of%20the%20other%20community.%20And%20barring%20interludes%20of%20internecine%20violence%2C%20the%20three%20communities%20have%20lived%20together%20with%20peace%20and%20goodwill.%20It%20is%20this%20long%20history%20of%20inter-ethnic%20peace%20that%20the%202023%20warlike%20clashes%20threaten%20to%20destroy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Meitei%20are%20the%20dominant%20group%20in%20Manipur%2C%20in%20population%20share%20(53%25)%20as%20well%20as%20politically%20and%20economically.%20They%20reside%20mainly%20in%20the%20Imphal%20valley%2C%20which%20comprises%20just%2010%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20geography.%20The%20Meitei%20trace%20their%20ancestry%20in%20the%20Imphal%20valley%20at%20least%20to%202000%20years%20back.%20The%20kingdom%20was%20ruled%20by%20one%20of%20the%20longest%20unbroken%20dynasties%20of%20the%20world%2C%20the%20Ningthouja%2C%20from%2033%20AD.%20The%20name%20Manipur%20came%20later.%20The%20kingdom%20was%20Kangleipak%2C%20renamed%20in%201724%20by%20the%20king%20now%20converted%20to%20Hinduism%2C%20who%20chose%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fhistory-of-it%2Fstory%2Fmanipur-violence-when-did-kukis-reach-manipur-and-how-past-is-shaping-states-present-2416215-2023-08-04%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESanskrit%20name%20Manipur%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20boundaries%20of%20the%20kingdom%20sometimes%20included%20the%20surrounding%20hills%2C%20and%20went%20so%20far%20as%20the%20Irrawady%20river%20in%20Myanmar.%20But%20for%20the%20greater%20part%20of%20its%20history%20of%20two%20millennia%20before%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20British%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fhistory-of-it%2Fstory%2Fmanipur-violence-when-did-kukis-reach-manipur-and-how-past-is-shaping-states-present-2416215-2023-08-04%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eit%20was%20confined%20to%20the%20valley%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Finclusion-of-meiteis-in-st-list-rejected-in-1982-2001-historical-documents-kept-from-manipur-hc%5C%22%3E%20Inclusion%20of%20Meiteis%20in%20ST%20List%20Rejected%20in%201982%2C%202001%2C%20Historical%20Documents%20Kept%20From%20Manipur%20HC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20rulers%20and%20people%20of%20the%20Imphal%20valley%20followed%20the%20indigenous%20animistic%20faith%20of%20Sanahism%20until%20the%2018%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century.%20The%20king%20in%201704%20converted%20to%20the%20Hindu%20faith%2C%20and%20large%20sections%20of%20the%20people%20also%20adopted%20the%20Vaishnavite%20faith.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Naga%20and%20Kuki-Zomi%20are%20not%20two%20homogenous%20tribes%20but%20are%20clusters%20of%20many%20tribes%2C%20listed%20as%2034%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idsa.in%2Fissuebrief%2FThe-Unfolding-Kuki-Meitei-Conflict-pdas-260523%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Constitution%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20Nagas%2C%2017%25%20of%20the%20population%20of%20present-day%20Manipur%2C%20inhabited%20the%20northern%20hill%20ranges%20for%20almost%20as%20long%20as%20the%20Meitei%20people%20in%20the%20valley.%20The%20Kukis%2C%20around%2026%25%2C%20are%20admittedly%20of%20more%20recent%20origin%2C%20but%20how%20recent%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20current%20dispute.%20The%20first%20archival%20mention%20of%20the%20Kuki%20in%20Manipur%20is%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fhistory-of-it%2Fstory%2Fmanipur-violence-when-did-kukis-reach-manipur-and-how-past-is-shaping-states-present-2416215-2023-08-04%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBritish%20colonial%20records%20in%201777%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20is%20alleged%20that%20the%20British%20encouraged%20the%20settlements%20of%20the%20Kuki%20people%20in%20the%20hills%20of%20Manipur%20to%20provide%20a%20counter%20to%20the%20more%20aggressive%20Naga%20tribes%2C%20but%20it%20is%20also%20true%20that%20the%20Kukis%20were%20enemies%20of%20the%20colonial%20British%20and%20therefore%20colonial%20writings%20cannot%20be%20taken%20at%20face%20value.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20these%20three%20large%20ethnic%20clusters%2C%20the%20valley%20also%20is%20home%20to%20Muslim%20Meitei%20(called%20Pangal)%20who%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20migrated%20in%20the%2017%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%20from%20Sylhet%2C%20and%20now%20are%208%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20and%20also%20the%20Gurkhas%20and%20immigrants%20from%20mainland%20India.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20Manipur%20was%20invaded%20by%20Burma%20in%201819%2C%20the%20king%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20British%20for%20protection%20and%20Manipur%20became%2C%20between%201826%20to%201891%2C%20a%20protectorate%20of%20the%20British%2C%20and%20from%201891%20a%20princely%20state%20of%20the%20British%20Empire.%20It%20signed%20an%20annexation%20treaty%20with%20India%20in%201947%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fhistory-of-it%2Fstory%2Fmanipur-violence-when-did-kukis-reach-manipur-and-how-past-is-shaping-states-present-2416215-2023-08-04%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emerged%20with%20the%20Indian%20union%20in%201949%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20interesting%20that%20before%20its%20annexation%2C%20the%20briefly%20independent%20state%20of%20Manipur%20had%20passed%20the%20State%20Constitution%20Act%20in%20May%201947%2C%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20in%20Asia.%20The%20king%20two%20years%20earlier%20had%20converted%20Manipur%20into%20a%20democratic%20constitutional%20monarchy.%20The%20constitution%20was%20progressive%20in%20its%20representation%20of%20various%20communities%3A%20it%20created%20three%20categories%20that%20it%20termed%20General%2C%20Hill%20and%20Mohamaden%20(Muslim)%2C%20and%20provided%20for%20elections%20to%20the%20legislature%20for%20these%20three%20groups%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkapilarambam.blogspot.com%2F2016%2F08%2Fmanipur-state-constitution-act-1947.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eratio%20of%2030%2C%2018%20and%203%20respectively%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Another%20interesting%20fact%20of%20this%20history%20is%20that%20when%20the%20legislature%20of%20Manipur%20passed%20a%20resolution%20opposing%20the%20merger%20of%20Manipur%20with%20the%20union%20of%20India%2C%20the%20Speaker%20was%20a%20Kuki%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fe-pao.net%2FGP.asp%3Fsrc%3D18..070613.jun13%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETC%20Tainkhan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EManipur%20%E2%80%93%20a%20site%20of%20entrenched%20violence%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20as%20though%20violence%20is%20new%20to%20Manipur.%20The%20state%20witnessed%20some%20of%20the%20earliest%20insurgent%20movements%20in%20North-East%20India%2C%20of%20both%20Naga%20and%20Meitei%20militant%20groups%2C%20not%20long%20after%20the%20merger%20of%20the%20princely%20state%20of%20Manipur%20into%20the%20union%20of%20India%20in%201949.%20Kuki%20militant%20groups%20rose%20only%20from%20the%201990s.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20militant%20groups%20are%20organised%20around%20ethnic%20lines%20of%20the%20three%20main%20ethnic%20clusters%20of%20the%20state%20%E2%80%93%20Meitei%2C%20Kuki%20and%20Naga.%20Their%20demands%20have%20ranged%20from%20independence%20from%20the%20Indian%20state%20to%20various%20grades%20of%20self-rule%20within%20the%20Indian%20union%2C%20and%20they%20have%20targeted%20both%20the%20Indian%20state%20and%20other%20ethnic%20communities%20within%20Manipur.%20While%20the%20Nagas%20and%20Kukis%20fought%20a%20bloody%20series%20of%20ethnic%20battles%20in%20the%201990s%20resulting%20in%20more%20than%20400%20deaths%2C%202023%20sees%20the%20first%20major%20clash%20between%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20people.%20(Kuki%20leaders%20recall%20that%20Kuki%20chiefs%20sent%20300%20volunteers%20to%20support%20the%20Meitei%20king%20in%20his%20opposition%20to%20the%20merger%20as%20proof%20that%20the%20Kuki%20people%20were%20historically%20not%20enemies%20but%20supporters%20of%20the%20Meiteis).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04223216%2Fimage-968.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22810%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04223216%2Fimage-968.png%20810w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04223216%2Fimage-968-300x131.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-651750%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22355%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFile%20photo%20of%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%40MangteC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Naga%20militant%20groups%20have%20engaged%20in%20extended%20peace%20negotiations%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%20in%20recent%20years.%20The%20government%20of%20India%20entered%20into%20a%20Suspension%20of%20Operations%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crisisgroup.org%2Fasia%2Fsouth-asia%2Findia%2Fethnic-clashes-roiling-manipur-pose-test-indias-modi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eagreement%20with%20the%20Kuki%20militant%20groups%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%202008.%20The%20Meitei%20groups%20have%20not%20been%20part%20of%20any%20peace%20agreement.%20The%20present%20chief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh%20has%20not%20hidden%20his%20closeness%20%E2%80%93%20and%20some%20suggest%20active%20patronage%20%E2%80%93%20to%20the%20Meitei%20militias%20Arongal%20Tenngol%20and%20Meitei%20Leepun%2C%20who%20have%20reportedly%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20the%20present%20conflict.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20indicator%20of%20how%20deeply%20entrenched%20the%20violence%20in%20post-merger%20Manipur%20is%20that%20although%20Manipur%20is%20home%20to%20just%200.2%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20as%20many%20as%2038%25%20of%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E(UAPA)%20cases%20in%20the%20country%20registered%20between%202014%20and%202020%20were%20in%20Manipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EData%20from%20the%20National%20Crimes%20Research%20Bureau%20reveal%20that%20in%20this%20period%20while%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20cases%20registered%20under%20the%20UAPA%20were%20in%20Manipur%20(2%2C595)%2C%20this%20was%20followed%20quite%20distantly%20by%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20(1%2C202)%20and%20Assam%20(1%2C071).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%20there%20are%20an%20estimated%2030%20militant%20groups%20in%20Manipur%2C%20but%20for%20many%20years%20most%20of%20these%20have%20been%20dormant%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Naga%20groups%20in%20long%20drawn-out%20peace%20talks%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20and%20the%20Kuki%20groups%20in%20a%20tripartite%20Suspension%20of%20Operations%20(SoO)%20agreement.%20Some%20operate%20from%20across%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crisisgroup.org%2Fasia%2Fsouth-asia%2Findia%2Fethnic-clashes-roiling-manipur-pose-test-indias-modi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eporous%20border%20in%20Myanmar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20lit%20the%20fires%20in%20Manipur%20in%202023%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20this%20long%20history%20of%20internecine%20and%20anti-state%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%20ever%20since%20its%20merger%20with%20the%20Indian%20union%2C%20what%20had%20contributed%20to%20the%20unprecedented%20ferocity%20of%20the%20present%20combat%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20accounts%20begin%20with%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court%20ruling%20for%20suggesting%20ST%20status%20for%20the%20Meitei%2C%20the%20state-wide%20protests%20by%20Kuki%20organisations%20against%20this%2C%20and%20violent%20counter-protests%20by%20the%20Meitei.%20But%20these%20actually%20were%20only%20the%20matchsticks%20that%20lit%20a%20fire%20for%20which%20the%20fuel%20had%20already%20been%20dangerously%20(and%20wantonly)%20spilt.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20paramount%20responsibility%20for%20pushing%20Manipur%2C%20and%20with%20it%20the%20country%2C%20to%20the%20brink%20must%20rest%20most%20on%20the%20shoulders%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20for%20his%20open%20unapologetic%20partisanship%2C%20his%20frequent%20resort%20to%20deliberately%20provocative%20public%20statements%20and%20actions%2C%20and%20for%20his%20wanton%20refusal%20to%20disarm%2C%20charge%20and%20arrest%20those%20openly%20spreading%20hate%20and%20lethal%20violence.%20And%20with%20him%2C%20the%20union%20government%20is%20responsible%20for%20not%20reining%20him%20in%2C%20or%20better%2C%20replacing%20him%2C%20and%20for%20not%20ensuring%20that%20sufficient%20forces%20are%20deployed%20to%20disarm%20the%20civilian%20populations%20and%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20all%20people%20of%20every%20identity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F05155939%2FUntitled-design-18.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F05155939%2FUntitled-design-18.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F05155939%2FUntitled-design-18-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F05155939%2FUntitled-design-18-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-651837%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPM%20Modi%20and%20CM%20Biren%20Singh.%20In%20the%20background%20is%20a%20video%20screengrab%20of%20cars%20burning%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20when%20he%20was%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20he%20became%20infamous%20(or%20popular%2C%20depending%20on%20who%20was%20making%20the%20evaluation)%20for%20his%20anti-Kuki%20rhetoric.%20These%20became%20more%20strident%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20midsummer%20bloodbath%20of%202023%2C%20and%20in%20the%20months%20after%20it%20broke%20out.%20Outlook%20India%20spoke%20to%20many%20people%2C%20including%20BJP%20Kuki%20MLAs%2C%20who%20described%20the%20chief%20minister%20as%20%E2%80%9Cprejudiced%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Canti-Kuki%E2%80%9D.%20Even%20Meitei%20commentators%20like%20Pradip%20Phajouban%20said%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20provocative%20discourse%20over%20the%20last%20two%20or%20three%20years%20made%20the%20Kukis%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fnational%2Fwhy-kuki-meitei-conflict-in-manipur-is-more-than-just-and-ethnic-clash-news-290306%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Every%20sensitive%2C%20pushed%20to%20the%20wall%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20strand%20of%20his%20rhetoric%20is%20to%20stigmatise%20the%20Kuki%20people%20as%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigrants%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cforeigners%E2%80%9D.%20This%20is%20an%20obvious%20canard%2C%20as%20pointed%20out%20by%20the%20Editors%E2%80%99%20Guild%20in%20their%20report%20after%20visiting%20the%20state%2C%20because%20the%20decennial%20censuses%20from%201901%20to%202011%20have%20not%20shown%20any%20unusual%20rise%20in%20the%20non-Naga%20tribal%20population.%20The%20military%20coup%20in%20neighbouring%20Myanmar%20led%20Chin%20minorities%20to%20flee%20into%20neighbouring%20states%20like%20Mizoram%20and%20an%20estimated%204%2C000%20to%20Manipur.%20But%20it%20is%20unfair%20to%20use%20this%20to%20tar%20all%20Kuki%20residents%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feditorsguild.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEGI-report-on-Manipur.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eillegal%20foreigners%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20second%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cothering%E2%80%9D%20discourse%20led%20and%20fuelled%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20is%20of%20Kukis%20being%20%E2%80%9Cpoppy%20cultivators%E2%80%9D%20(or%20worse%2C%20narco-terrorists)%20engaged%20in%20transnational%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crisisgroup.org%2Fasia%2Fsouth-asia%2Findia%2Fethnic-clashes-roiling-manipur-pose-test-indias-modi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edrug%20trade%20centred%20in%20Myanmar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20responsible%20for%20the%20spread%20of%20drug%20addiction%20like%20a%20silent%20epidemic%20across%20the%20valley.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20vast%20tracks%20of%20fields%20in%20the%20hills%20grow%20poppies%2C%20and%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20poppy%20farmers%20are%20Kuki.%20But%20successive%20state%20governments%2C%20including%20the%20present%20one%2C%20have%20done%20little%20to%20halt%20this%20cultivation.%20People%20estimate%20the%20volume%20of%20the%20illegal%20drug%20trade%20in%20the%20state%20at%20around%20Rs%2050%2C000%20crore%20(incidentally%20much%20higher%20than%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprobe.in%2Fcolumns%2Fmanipur-violence-why-doesnt-the-violence-stop-here%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eentire%20budget%20of%20the%20state%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E)%3B%20and%20there%20is%20no%20credible%20claim%20that%20the%20processing%20and%20trafficking%20of%20the%20drugs%20are%20enterprises%20operated%20and%20owned%20by%20Kuki%20people.%20The%20responsibility%20for%20the%20massive%20illegal%20drug%20industry%20lies%20elsewhere%2C%20including%20with%20powerful%20men%20and%20women%20in%20Imphal%20and%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdespite-repeated-requests-pm-modi-avoids-meeting-manipur-bjp-mlas%5C%22%3E%20Despite%20Repeated%20Requests%2C%20PM%20Modi%20Avoids%20Meeting%20Manipur%20BJP%20MLAs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20all%20of%20this%20unfolded%2C%20the%20temperature%20of%20hate%20propaganda%20in%20the%20popular%20discourse%20against%20the%20Kuki%20people%20was%20also%20raised%20dangerously.%20There%20was%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20a%20systematic%20attack%20on%20the%20history%20of%20Kukis%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESangai%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20largest%20circulated%20newspaper%20in%20Manipur.%20A%20new%20joint%20organisation%20of%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Tangkhul%20people%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98Federation%20of%20Haomee%E2%80%99%20demonised%20the%20Kukis.%20To%20all%20of%20this%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20his%20government%20never%20reacted.%20These%20too%20were%20preparatory%20to%20the%20current%20violence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20even%20more%20than%20this%20hate%20discourse%2C%20what%20triggered%20further%20existential%20insecurities%20and%20fear%20among%20the%20Kuki%20people%20were%20a%20series%20of%20imperious%20public%20actions%20clearly%20targeted%20at%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImportant%20among%20these%20was%20what%20could%20only%20be%20described%20as%20the%20weaponising%20of%20provisions%20and%20powers%20of%20the%20state%20government%20under%20the%20Hills%20Area%20Committee%20Act%20of%201972.%20The%20Kuki%20people%20continue%20to%20resort%20to%20their%20customary%20modes%20of%20shifting%20cultivation%20in%20the%20forested%20hills%20as%20they%20have%20for%20centuries%2C%20moving%20from%20one%20forest%20habitat%20to%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Editors%20Guild%20reports%20that%20without%20following%20proper%20procedure%20as%20laid%20down%20in%20this%20Act%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20declared%20parts%20of%20Hills%20as%20%E2%80%98reserved%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98protected%E2%80%99%20forests%20and%20%E2%80%98wetland%20reserves%E2%80%99.%20All%20land%20owner-ship%20documents%20within%20these%20areas%20were%20cancelled%20and%20a%20drive%20started%20to%20evict%20them%20in%20December%202022%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20fuelled%20Kuki%20anger%20more%20%E2%80%9Cis%20that%20the%20forest%20surveys%2C%20inquiries%2C%20evictions%20and%20demolitions%20were%20carried%20out%20only%20in%20the%20non-Naga%20inhabited%20tribal%20areas%2C%20once%20again%20leading%20the%20Kuki%20community%20to%20believe%20that%20it%20was%20being%20singled%20out%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F02171816%2F64759832_1242658312578641_1086289618199904256_n.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F02171816%2F64759832_1242658312578641_1086289618199904256_n.jpeg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F02171816%2F64759832_1242658312578641_1086289618199904256_n-300x163.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-651373%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22543%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EManipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FN.%20Biren%20Singh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20led%20inevitably%20to%20violent%20confrontations%20in%20the%20early%20months%20of%202023%20between%20the%20state%20authorities%20and%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20which%20had%20been%20living%20in%20these%20villages.%20A%20committee%20of%20the%20state%20government%20headed%20by%20the%20chief%20secretary%20on%20April%203%2C%202023%2C%20cancelled%20all%20land%2Fproperty%20deeds%20and%20recognition%20of%20villages%20within%20the%20designated%20reserved%20and%20protected%20forest%20areas%2C%20without%20any%20rehabilitation%20plan%20for%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feditorsguild.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEGI-report-on-Manipur.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eevicted%20tribal%20population%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20then%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20highly%20publicised%20%E2%80%9Cwar%20on%20drugs%E2%80%9D.%20Experts%20tell%20us%20that%20in%20this%20highly%20lucrative%20trans-national%20drug%20trade%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdrugs%20of%20choice%20are%3A%20heroin%2C%20brown%20sugar%2C%20prescription%20painkillers%2C%20cough%20syrups%20and%20Yaba%20or%20WIY%20(%E2%80%9CWorld%20is%20yours%E2%80%9D)%20pills%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20exclusive%20focus%20was%20only%20on%20poppy%20growing%20which%20targeted%20the%20poorest%20poppy%20cultivators%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20Kuki%2C%20to%20the%20wilful%20neglect%20of%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20other%20components%20of%20the%20drug%20trade%2C%20the%20smuggling%20of%20synthetics%20to%20Myanmar%20and%20the%20smuggling%20in%20of%20drugs%20and%20their%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feditorsguild.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEGI-report-on-Manipur.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edistribution%20through%20Manipur%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20yet%20another%20series%20of%20openly%20provocative%20official%20moves%2C%20in%20March%202023%2C%20the%20state%20government%20peremptorily%20withdrew%20from%20the%20tripartite%20Suspension%20of%20Operations%20(SoO)%20agreement%20with%20the%20Kuki%20militants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20effectively%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20which%20was%20suddenly%2C%20summarily%20and%20unilaterally%20terminated%2C%20without%20explanation%20or%20discussion%20with%20the%20Manipuri%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20then%20went%20on%20to%20remove%20the%20application%20of%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20Special%20Powers%20Act%20(AFSPA)%20selectively%20only%20from%20the%20Imphal%20Valley%20and%20not%20the%20hill%20districts.%20As%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20notes%2C%20this%20was%20obviously%20partisan%20because%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Kuki%20insurgent%20groups%20were%20in%20peace%20talks%20with%20the%20Union%20while%20the%20Meitei%20insurgents%20active%20in%20the%20Imphal%20Valley%20were%20outside%20any%20process%20of%20negotiation%20for%20peace%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20made%20no%20secret%20of%20his%20closeness%20with%20Meitei%20militias%20like%20the%20Arambai%20Tenngol%2C%20even%20on%20occasion%20posing%20for%20photographs%20with%20the%20militants.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20retrospect%2C%20this%20was%20seen%20by%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20tribals%20as%20a%20partisan%20move%20in%20preparation%20for%20violence%20against%20the%20Kukis%2C%20which%20came%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feditorsguild.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEGI-report-on-Manipur.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efew%20weeks%20later%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20against%20this%20background%20that%20the%20provocation%20and%20rage%20of%20the%20Kuki%20people%20can%20be%20understood%20against%20the%20decision%20of%20a%20single-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20high%20court.%20Tellingly%2C%20the%20state%20government%20did%20not%20appeal%20against%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20directive.%20This%20was%20the%20proverbial%20straw%20that%20broke%20the%20camel%E2%80%99s%20back.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETribal%20student%20organisations%20resolved%20to%20organise%20protest%20marches%20in%20all%20district%20headquarters%20on%20May%203%20under%20the%20conciliatory%20theme%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idsa.in%2Fissuebrief%2FThe-Unfolding-Kuki-Meitei-Conflict-pdas-260523%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECome%20Let%20Us%20Reason%20Together%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERallies%20were%20held%20in%2010%20of%20the%2016%20districts%20of%20the%20state.%20But%20in%20some%20of%20these%20rallies%2C%20clashes%20broke%20out%20between%20people%20of%20the%20two%20communities%2C%20and%20the%20state%20exploded%20in%20flames.%20The%20same%20night%2C%20homes%20and%20churches%20of%20Kuki%20residents%20of%20the%20Imphal%20valley%20were%20vandalised%20and%20burnt%20by%20radical%20gangs%20of%20Meitei%20young%20men%2C%20killing%20many%20including%20women%20and%20children.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20next%20few%20days%2C%20massive%20counter-rallies%20were%20organised%20by%20the%20Meiteis%2C%20including%20women%20who%20often%20blocked%20attempts%20by%20security%20forces%20to%20rescue%20people%20and%20protect%20shrines%20and%20property.%20Killings%20and%20horrific%20acts%20of%20sexual%20violence%20followed.%20The%20clashes%20quickly%20spread%20to%20the%20hills%20where%20armed%20mobs%20destroyed%20villages%20and%20homes%20of%20the%20Meitei%20people.%20Burning%20down%20of%20almost%20all%20the%20Meitei%20settlements%20in%20Churachandpur%20and%20Moreh%20by%20the%20Kuki%20militants%20further%20triggered%20the%20cycle%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFive%20months%20later%2C%20as%20I%20write%20this%2C%20the%20killings%20continue%20with%20numbing%20constancy.%20At%20least%20200%20people%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20an%20uncounted%20number%20are%20injured%20and%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20own%20admission%2C%20there%20are%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idsa.in%2Fissuebrief%2FThe-Unfolding-Kuki-Meitei-Conflict-pdas-260523%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehundreds%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20of%20complaints%20of%20sexual%20violence.%20Almost%2060%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20rendered%20homeless%20as%20Kuki%20homes%20and%20habitations%20in%20Meitei%20majority%20areas%2C%20and%20Meitei%20homes%20and%20villages%20in%20Kuki%20majority%20hill%20tracts%20have%20been%20destroyed%20and%20razed%20to%20the%20ground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20both%20communities%20have%20both%20perpetrated%20and%20suffered%20horrific%20losses%20of%20life%20and%20property%2C%20it%20would%20be%20fair%20to%20underline%20that%20the%20losses%20are%20much%20greater%20among%20the%20Kuki%20people%2C%20probably%20because%20of%20tacit%20or%20open%20state%20support.%20At%20least%20300%20churches%20have%20been%20vandalised%20and%20burnt%20down.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThrough%20all%20of%20this%2C%20the%20state%20has%20remained%20culpably%20absent%20from%20the%20discharge%20of%20its%20constitutional%20duties.%20The%20governments%20of%20India%20and%20Manipur%20are%20unable%20(or%20unwilling)%20to%20disarm%20civilian%20populations%20and%20militant%20militias%2C%20and%20to%20charge%2C%20arrest%20and%20prosecute%20people%20responsible%20for%20horrific%20murders%20and%20rapes%2C%20the%20looting%20of%20armouries%2C%20and%20the%20burning%20and%20looting%20of%20homes%20and%20villages%2C%20in%20which%20no%20one%20was%20spared%3A%20the%20home%20of%20even%20a%20union%20minister%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20cabinet%20was%20burned%20down%20in%20Imphal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20is%20also%20absent%20from%20its%20duty%20to%20extend%20relief%20to%20the%2060%2C000%20internally%20displaced%20people%20whose%20houses%20and%20villages%20have%20been%20razed%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20colossal%20humanitarian%20crisis%20in%20what%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkarwanemohabbat.substack.com%2Fp%2Fthe-humanitarian-crisis-in-manipur%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebecome%20a%20war%20zone%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20might%20of%20the%20Indian%20state%20seems%20singularly%20unequal%20to%20the%20challenge%20of%20restoring%20peace%20and%20security%20in%20this%20tiny%20but%20enormously%20sensitive%20frontier%20state%20that%20shares%20a%20long%20border%20with%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20violence%20began%2C%20the%20state%20government%20ticked%20the%20mandatory%20boxes%2C%20by%20ordering%20a%20curfew%20and%20directing%20District%20Magistrates%20to%20issue%20shoot-at-sight%20orders%20in%20extreme%20cases.%20But%20in%20practice%2C%20none%20of%20this%20was%20enforced.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20done%20nothing%20to%20prevent%20men%20brandishing%20modern%20and%20presumably%20unlicensed%20weapons%20from%20patrolling%20the%20streets%2C%20nothing%20to%20disarm%20them%2C%20and%20nothing%20to%20investigate%2C%20charge%20and%20detain%20those%20named%20in%20police%20complaints%20for%20murder%2C%20rape%20and%20arson.%20Bunkers%20lined%20with%20sandbags%20manned%20by%20heavily%20armed%20men%20have%20come%20up%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cborder%E2%80%9D%20of%20a%20state%20that%20has%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crisisgroup.org%2Fasia%2Fsouth-asia%2Findia%2Fethnic-clashes-roiling-manipur-pose-test-indias-modi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eeffectively%20partitioned%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EClose%20to%20the%20checkpoints%20along%20this%20border%20are%20clusters%20of%20women%20groups%2C%20the%20Meira%20Paibi%20(revered%20for%20their%20iconic%20protests%20against%20killings%20and%20rape%20by%20army%20personnel)%20on%20the%20Meitei%20side%2C%20and%20Kuki%20women%20groups%20on%20the%20other.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20police%20and%20paramilitary%20forces%20in%20the%20state%20have%20also%20been%20perilously%20divided%20on%20ethnic%20grounds.%20The%20local%20police%20is%20largely%20Meitei%20and%20does%20not%20hide%20their%20partisanship.%20The%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20a%20paramilitary%20formation%20controlled%20by%20the%20Indian%20army%20is%20being%20stigmatised%20for%20performing%20its%20duty%20of%20protecting%20the%20Kukis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20long%20history%20of%20this%3A%20the%20Meitei%20version%20is%20that%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20and%20Kuki%20militants%20partnered%20in%20counter%20insurgency%20operations%20against%20Naga%20and%20Meitei%20insurgent%20groups%3B%20and%20that%20Kuki%20militants%20under%20the%20Suspension%20of%20Operations%20agreement%20draw%20a%20monthly%20salary%20from%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20sent%20a%20legal%20notice%20to%20a%20Meitei%20leader%20for%20his%20allegations%20that%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20was%20partisan.%20The%20Manipur%20police%20filed%20FIRs%20against%20Assam%20Rifles%20soldiers%20for%20allegedly%20blocking%20their%20way%20with%20armoured%20vehicles%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-history%2Fassam-rifles-manipur-police-filed-fir-8884517%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehelping%20Kuki%20militants%20to%20escape%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20feeding%20into%20the%20popular%20Meitei%20narrative%20that%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20soldiers%20are%20shielding%20Kuki%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fnews%2Fmanipur-divided-state-pits-one-force-against-other-181571%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enarco-terrorists%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Assam%20Rifles%20argue%20that%20they%20are%20being%20pilloried%20only%20because%20they%20escorted%20endangered%20Kuki%20people%20to%20safety%2C%20and%20patrol%20the%20border%20blocking%20Meitei%20militants%20from%20executing%20killing%20missions%20into%20the%20hills.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeitei%20groups%20led%20by%20the%20Meitei%20Paibi%20have%20been%20demanding%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20from%20all%20of%20Manipur%2C%20and%20in%20the%20course%20of%20their%20protests%20locked%20the%20gates%20of%20central%20government%20offices.%20Whatever%20may%20have%20been%20their%20role%20in%20the%20present%20conflict%2C%20it%20must%20be%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20Manipuri%20people%20have%20long%20hated%20the%20Assam%20Rifles.%20It%20was%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20rape%20and%20brutal%20murder%20of%20a%20Meitei%20woman%20Thongam%20Monorama%20that%20led%20to%20the%20iconic%20protest%20by%20women%20of%20the%20Meitei%20Paibi%20in%202004%20when%20they%20stripped%20naked%20before%20the%20headquarters%20of%20the%20Assam%20Rifles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeitei%20groups%20also%20met%20defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-meitei-group-meets-rajnath-singh-over-removal-of-assam-rifles-101694752006123.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epress%20this%20demand%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20chief%20minister%20assured%20representatives%20of%20the%20Meitei%20Paibi%20that%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20would%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnenow.in%2Fnorth-east-news%2Fmanipur%2Famid-protest-manipur-cm-assures-meira-paibis-of-withdrawal-of-assam-rifles-from-state.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eindeed%20be%20withdrawn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20the%20state%20in%20September.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20state%20cabinet%20ordered%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fnorth-east-india%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-cabinet-resolves-to-replace-assam-rifles-check-post-by-state-police%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereplacement%20of%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20the%20local%20police%20in%20manning%20a%20crucial%20border%20checkpoint.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20background%2C%20the%20initiative%20by%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20after%20his%20sole%20visit%20to%20Manipur%20after%20the%20violence%20broke%20out%2C%20to%20establish%20a%20unified%20command%20of%20police%20and%20paramilitary%20forces%20under%20the%20chief%20minister%20was%20still-born.%20The%20prime%20minister%20has%20not%20visited%20Manipur%20even%20five%20months%20into%20the%20conflict%2C%20and%2C%20until%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20his%20government%20in%20Parliament%2C%20did%20not%20make%20any%20public%20appeal%20for%20peace%20in%20Manipur%2C%20barring%20a%2030-second%20statement%20condemning%20the%20sexual%20violence.%20He%20brushed%20aside%20all%20demands%20to%20dismiss%20the%20state%20government%20or%20at%20least%20to%20replace%20the%20chief%20minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26170827%2FUntitled-design-16-2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26170827%2FUntitled-design-16-2.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26170827%2FUntitled-design-16-2-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26170827%2FUntitled-design-16-2-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665264%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EVideo%20screengrab%20showing%20PM%20Modi%20with%20his%20back%20to%20the%20cameras%20after%20he%20addressed%20the%20Manipur%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20also%20questions%20about%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20in%20stoking%20majoritarian%20sentiments%20among%20the%20Meitei%20people.%20In%20recent%20years%20the%20valley%20has%20witnessed%20the%20rise%20of%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98Meiteism%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20a%20concerted%20effort%20to%20revive%20Meitei%20identity%2C%20religion%20and%20culture%20often%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fnational%2Fwhy-kuki-meitei-conflict-in-manipur-is-more-than-just-and-ethnic-clash-news-290306%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ealigned%20with%20Hinduism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20a%20Meitei%20sub-nationalism%20often%20converging%20with%20Hindutva%20nationalism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWithin%20this%20revival%20is%20a%20strong%20assertion%20of%20indigeneity%20and%20primary%20belonging%20%E2%80%93%20the%20idea%20that%20Manipur%20is%20the%20land%20of%20the%20Meitei%2C%20and%20they%20are%20threatened%20by%20the%20alleged%20growing%20numbers%20of%20Kuki%20tribes%20of%20Christian%20faith.%20There%20is%20also%20fueling%20a%20narrative%20of%20alleged%20proselytising%20by%20the%20Christian%20church.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnalysts%20sometimes%20compare%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20of%202023%20to%20the%20Gujarat%20communal%20carnage%20of%202002.%20The%20comparison%20is%20apt%20only%20up%20to%20a%20point.%20In%20both%2C%20the%20state%20government%20was%20aggressively%20majoritarian%20and%20the%20leadership%20bellicose%20in%20its%20communal%20or%20ethnic%20partisanship%3B%20in%20both%2C%20the%20state%20government%20did%20nothing%20to%20protect%20the%20targeted%20minorities%2C%20and%20to%20extend%20relief%20or%20to%20secure%20to%20them%20legal%20justice%3B%20and%20in%20both%2C%20the%20state%20leadership%20was%20stubbornly%20protected%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%20But%20the%20resemblance%20ends%20here.%20Imagine%20Gujarat%20in%202002%20if%20the%20Muslim%20victims%20also%20fought%20back%20and%20both%20sides%20were%20armed%20to%20their%20teeth%20with%20weapons%20of%20modern%20warfare.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmohan-bhagwat-comments-manipur-violence-northeast-puzzle%5C%22%3EMohan%20Bhagwat%E2%80%99s%20Comments%20on%20Manipur%20Violence%20Show%20Northeast%20Remains%20a%20Puzzle%20That%20RSS%20Can%E2%80%99t%20Solve%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20this%20brings%20me%20to%20what%20is%20arguably%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20most%20culpable%20contribution%20to%20converting%20what%20could%20have%20been%20a%20bloody%20ethnic%20battle%20of%20the%20kind%20that%20the%20state%20has%20seen%20too%20often%20in%20the%20past%2C%20into%20a%20civil%20war%20%E2%80%93%20the%20looting%20of%20armouries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20the%20march%2C%20and%20repeatedly%20after%20it%2C%20Meitei%20mobs%20stormed%20police%20armouries%20and%20absconded%20with%20an%20estimated%204%2C000%20modern%20weapons%20including%20assault%20rifles%2C%20long-range%20guns%2C%2051%20mm%20mortars%20and%20half%20a%20million%20bullets.%20There%20is%20no%20evidence%20that%20the%20Manipur%20police%2C%20most%20of%20them%20of%20Meitei%20identity%2C%20used%20any%20significant%20force%20to%20prevent%20this%20pillage%2C%20which%20has%20continued%20to%20recur.%20It%20is%20alleged%20that%20Kuki%20police%20persons%20in%20the%20valley%20permitted%20a%20similar%20looting%20of%20arms%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crisisgroup.org%2Fasia%2Fsouth-asia%2Findia%2Fethnic-clashes-roiling-manipur-pose-test-indias-modi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebut%20on%20a%20much%20smaller%20scale%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20date%2C%20only%20a%20small%20fraction%20of%20these%20arms%20have%20been%20recovered.%20It%20is%20this%20plunder%20with%20impunity%20of%20state%20armouries%20that%20has%20armed%20large%20civilian%20populations%20with%20lethal%20modern%20weapons%20on%20an%20scale%20unprecedented%20in%20independent%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20poisonous%20harvest%20of%20a%20majoritarian%20state%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20summary%2C%20the%20story%20that%20emerges%20out%20of%20Manipur%20is%20an%20extremely%20grim%20one.%20The%20agony%20of%20the%20Manipuri%20people%20is%20the%20poisonous%20harvest%20of%20a%20state%20that%20openly%20treats%20a%20segment%20of%20its%20own%20citizens%20as%20enemies.%20It%20begins%2C%20as%20we%20saw%2C%20with%20relentless%20runaway%20hate%20speech%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20himself%2C%20which%20stigmatises%20the%20Kuki%20citizens%20as%20illegal%20foreigners%20and%20narco-terrorists.%20With%20toxic%20falsehoods%20he%20builds%20a%20dark%20sceptre%20that%20haunts%20the%20popular%20Meitei%20imagination%2C%20of%20a%20shining%20Manipur%20home%20to%20the%20Meitei%20people%20for%20more%20than%20two%20centuries%20in%20grave%20danger%20of%20being%20overrun%20by%20alien%20immigrants%20pouring%20in%20from%20Myanmar.%20These%20unwanted%20aliens%2C%20according%20to%20his%20%E2%80%9Calternative%20truth%E2%80%9D%2C%20encroach%20and%20destroy%20Manipuri%20forests%2C%20grow%20poppies%20and%20ravage%20Meitei%20youth%20with%20their%20trade%20in%20opium%20and%20brown%20sugar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20then%20follows%20this%20up%20with%20a%20battery%20of%20public%20actions%2C%20directly%20targeting%20the%20Kuki%20minority%20in%20the%20state%20he%20has%20been%20elected%20to%20lead.%20He%20declares%20the%20forest%20abodes%20and%20shifting%20cultivation%20farms%2C%20inhabited%20for%20many%20generations%20by%20the%20Kuki%20people%2C%20as%20illegal%20and%20drives%20a%20campaign%20to%20free%20the%20forests%20from%20their%20%E2%80%9Cencroachments%E2%80%9D.%20He%20launches%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwar%20on%20drugs%E2%80%9D%20that%20targets%20only%20the%20lowest%20rung%20of%20poppy%20cultivators%2C%20mostly%20impoverished%20Kuki%20farmers%2C%20leaving%20unscathed%2C%20those%20engaged%20in%20the%20highly%20lucrative%20transnational%20drug%20trade.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20suddenly%20terminates%20without%20explanation%20the%20virtual%20ceasefire%20with%20Kuki%20militants%2C%20while%20not%20disguising%20his%20sympathies%20%E2%80%93%20and%20possible%20patronage%20%E2%80%93%20of%20Meitei%20militia.%20He%20does%20not%20appeal%20against%20a%20high%20court%20decision%20to%20recommend%20ST%20status%20to%20the%20Meitei%2C%20knowing%20how%20much%20this%20would%20stoke%20fears%20among%20the%20Kuki%20people%20and%20that%20this%20would%20open%20the%20doors%20for%20Meitei%20people%20to%20lawfully%20buy%20lands%20in%20the%20hills%2C%20pushing%20the%20minority%20further%20into%20the%20margins.%20And%20then%20his%20government%20stands%20by%20as%20militants%20loot%20police%20and%20paramilitary%20armouries%2C%20arming%20civilians%20to%20fight%20a%20civil%20war%20against%20another%20section%20of%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EA%20land%20of%20settled%20grief%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20critically%20wounded%20Manipur%20is%20a%20land%20of%20profound%20and%20settled%20grief.%20In%20relief%20camps%20of%20both%20communities%2C%20people%20spoke%20of%20their%20agony%20that%20their%20neighbours%20of%20generations%20had%20turned%20overnight%20into%20enemies.%20But%20an%20even%20greater%20sense%20of%20loss%20arose%20from%20their%20conviction%20that%20they%20would%20never%20be%20able%20to%20return%20to%20the%20only%20place%20they%20called%20home.%20A%20partition%20had%20been%20accomplished%2C%20a%20border%20had%20been%20drawn%20on%20their%20lands%2C%20as%20impenetrable%20and%20uncompromising%20as%20the%20one%20the%20country%20endured%20in%201947.%20And%20even%20more%20dangerously%2C%20in%20the%20hearts%20of%20ordinary%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F25175627%2Fimage-1085.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22772%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F25175627%2Fimage-1085.png%20772w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F25175627%2Fimage-1085-300x223.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-660062%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22575%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20silent%20march%20in%20Manipur%20on%20June%2024%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20relief%20camps%20that%20we%20visited%20in%20a%20four-day%20journey%20of%20the%20Karwan%20e%20Mohabbat%20to%20the%20state%20from%20July%2025%20to%2028%2C%20we%20found%20the%20state%20virtually%20absent.%20Communities%20pool%20donations%20every%20day%20to%20ensure%20that%20people%20are%20fed.%20We%20saw%20camps%20in%20the%20hills%20where%20children%20were%20eating%20just%20rice%20water%20with%20salt.%20The%20Karwan%20e%20Mohabbat%20prepared%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkarwanemohabbat.substack.com%2Fp%2Fthe-humanitarian-crisis-in-manipur%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edetailed%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20immense%20humanitarian%20crisis%20and%20what%20the%20state%20urgently%20needs%20to%20do.%20But%20little%20changes%2C%20as%20residents%20of%20the%20camps%20are%20offered%20little%20hope%20and%20reassurance%20that%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20broken%20pieces%20of%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20foreseeable%20future.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBarely%20a%20day%20passes%20without%20people%20with%20serious%20bullet%20injuries%20being%20wheeled%20into%20the%20single%20medical%20college%20in%20Churachandpur.%20Prior%20to%20the%20conflict%2C%20a%20one-hour%20road%20journey%20on%20an%20ambulance%20would%20transport%20them%20to%20the%20much%20better-equipped%20Imphal%20hospital.%20But%20today%2C%20this%20journey%20is%20impossible%20because%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cborder%E2%80%9D%20that%20implacably%20divides%20them.%20They%20sometimes%20struggle%20with%20a%2012-hour%20mountain%20road%20journey%20to%20Aizawl%2C%20but%20no%20life-support%20ambulance%20to%20keep%20their%20patients%20alive%20through%20this%20difficult%20journey%20is%20at%20hand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20conflict%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20halted%20supplies%20of%20food%20and%20medicine%20for%20patients%20and%20medical%20students.%20The%20battered%20community%20raises%20donations%20not%20just%20for%20the%20camps%2C%20but%20also%20to%20keep%20the%20public%20hospital%20functioning.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Wall%20of%20Remembrance%20has%20been%20erected%20in%20Churachandpur.%20On%20it%20are%20pasted%20pictures%20of%20every%20Kuki%20person%20who%20has%20been%20killed.%20You%20see%20on%20the%20wall%20faces%20of%20small%20children%2C%20women%2C%20old%20people%20and%20young%20men.%20The%20wall%20is%20surrounded%20by%20empty%20coffins.%20Every%20alternate%20day%20thousands%20of%20women%20dress%20in%20black%20and%20gather%20around%20the%20wall%20to%20collectively%20mourn.%20For%20five%20months%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20writing%2C%2096%20bodies%20lie%20in%20the%20mortuaries%20in%20Imphal%20and%20Churachandpur.%20The%20state%20government%20has%20not%20made%20safe%20arrangements%20for%20the%20families%20to%20travel%20to%20Imphal%20to%20identify%20the%20remains%20of%20their%20loved%20ones.%20And%20for%20those%20in%20Churachandpur%2C%20they%20long%20refused%20to%20bury%20them%20as%20a%20mark%20of%20their%20grief%20and%20protest.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20gentle%20pastor%20in%20Churachandpur%20Reverend%20Jangkholam%20Haokip%20barely%20finds%20time%20to%20sleep%20ever%20since%20the%20conflict%20broke%2C%20tirelessly%20organising%20food%20and%20medicines%20for%20the%20relief%20camps%20and%20hospital%2C%20and%20tending%20to%20the%20injured%20men%20brought%20in%20each%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20call%20him%20from%20time%20to%20time.%20One%20day%2C%20he%20almost%20broke%20down.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20do%20I%20tell%20our%20young%20people%3F%20What%20solace%20or%20hope%20can%20I%20offer%3F%20Do%20I%20tell%20them%20that%20we%20must%20just%20endure%20and%20wait%20to%20die%3F%20Each%20day%2C%20I%20search%20really%20hard%20to%20find%20some%20reason%20to%20hope.%20But%20I%20just%20cannot%20find%20even%20a%20single%20ray%20of%20hope%20for%20our%20future%20in%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fharsh-mander%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Harsh%20Mander%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarsh%20Mander%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20social%20worker%20and%20writer.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698851702000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F08131052%2FF7SQIIebEAAHp2K.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-a-land-of-settled-grief%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Th