ai%20Tenggol.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20independently%20confirm%20this%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELocals%20said%20the%20mob%20gathered%20at%20the%20palace%20compound%20of%20Leishemba%20Sanajaoba%2C%20the%20BJP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Manipur%20royal%20family%2C%20in%20the%20afternoon.%20Several%20were%20armed%2C%20they%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAround%206%3A25%20pm%2C%20the%20mob%20barged%20into%20the%20Manipur%20Rifles%20premises%20situated%20close%20to%20the%20Kangla%20Fort.%20What%20we%20heard%20is%20they%20did%20this%20because%20they%20wanted%20to%20seize%20arms.%20As%20we%20talk%20now%2C%20heavy%20firing%20is%20going%20on%20and%20reports%20of%20some%20killings%20have%20also%20come%20though%2C%20but%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20confirm%20it.%20What%20we%20have%20heard%20is%2C%20more%20Manipur%20Rifles%20stations%20have%20been%20targeted%20too%20to%20loot%20arms%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20eyewitness%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20Imphal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmob-surrounds-police-station-near-manipur-chief-ministers-office-cops-fire-in-air-4536465%5C%22%3ENDTV%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20fired%20several%20rounds%20in%20the%20air%20on%20Wednesday%20to%20disperse%20a%20mob%20that%20surrounded%20a%20police%20station%20near%20the%20Chief%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20in%20Imphal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Arambai%20Tenggol%2C%20said%20to%20be%20close%20to%20Sanajaoba%2C%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20carrying%20out%20several%20attacks%20on%20the%20Kuki%20community%20in%20Imphal%20during%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20that%20began%20in%20May.%20The%20immediate%20trigger%20for%20Tuesday%20evening%E2%80%99s%20mob%20attack%20on%20state%20police%20stations%20is%20said%20to%20be%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20police%20officer%20from%20the%20Meitei%20community%2C%20allegedly%20by%20Kuki%20militants%20a%20day%20ago%20in%20Teng