22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20solicitor%20general%20(SG)%20of%20India%20Tushar%20Mehta%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20November%201%2C%20defended%20the%20contentious%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20saying%20they%20protect%20the%20privacy%20of%20citizens%20who%20make%20such%20donations%20to%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20top%20court%20began%20hearing%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20scheme%2C%20which%20were%20first%20filed%20five%20years%20ago%20in%202018%2C%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20matter%20is%20being%20heard%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20B.R.%20Gavai%2C%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20SG%20emphasised%20the%20protection%20of%20%E2%80%9Cprivacy%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20affiliation%20of%20the%20citizens%20who%20make%20such%20donations%20to%20political%20parties%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Felectoral-bonds-anonymous-protect-privacy-political-affiliation-donor-sg-tushar-mehta-supreme-court%3Futm_source%3Dwebsite%26utm_medium%3Drelated-stories%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20per%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcitizens-have-no-fundamental-right-to-know-of-source-of-political-funding-ag-to-sc%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20in%20written%20submissions%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20said%20that%20citizens%20did%20not%20have%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20know%20the%20source%20of%20political%20funding.%20Attorney%20general%20R.%20Venkataramani%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cright%20to%20know%E2%80%9D%20must%20be%20subject%20to%20reasonable%20restrictions%20and%20can%20be%20exercised%20for%20specific%20ends%20or%20purposes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVenkataramani%20had%20also%20said%20in%20writing%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20would%20be%20entering%20the%20domain%20of%20policy%20if%20it%20tried%20to%20regulate%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESG%20Tushar%20Mehta%20said%20the%20scheme%20aims%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20the%20necessity%20for%20transparency%20and%20the%20need%20to%20safeguard%20donor%20confidentiality.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMehta%20stated%20that%20donors%20often%20resort%20to%20using%20unaccounted%20cash%20for%20political%20contributions%20due%20to%20their%20apprehension%20of%20potential%20victimisation%20or%20retribution%20from%20other%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMehta%20was%20cited%20by%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying%20that%20previous%20government%20initiatives%20aimed%20at%20cleaning%20up%20the%20source%20of%20political%20donations%2C%20such%20as%20tax%20exemptions%20and%20electoral%20trusts%2C%20had%20proven%20unsuccessful.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20electoral%20bond%20does%20not%20carry%20the%20name%20of%20the%20buyer%20or%20payee%20in%20order%20to%20protect%20the%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20privacy%20to%20its%20own%20political%20affiliation%20and%20to%20choose%20to%20fund%20a%20political%20party%20of%20its%20own%20choice%2C%20without%20the%20fear%20of%20being%20targeted%20or%20suffering%20vindicative%20repercussion%20for%20owning%20such%20a%20choice.%20It%20is%20in%20furtherance%20of%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20positive%20obligation%20to%20safeguard%20the%20privacy%20of%20its%20citizens%2C%20which%20necessarily%20includes%2C%20the%20citizens%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20informational%20privacy%2C%20including%20the%20right%20to%20secure%20the%20political%20affiliation%20of%20its%20citizens%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20submitted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20current%20scheme%20is%20a%20response%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdonor%20resistance%E2%80%9D%20and%20safeguarding%20their%20identities%2C%20said%20the%20SG.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMehta%20suggested%20that%20eliminating%20the%20confidentiality%20aspect%20of%20the%20scheme%20would%20render%20it%20ineffective%20and%20could%20potentially%20lead%20to%20a%20resurgence%20of%20cash-based%20political%20contributions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20present%20scheme%20is%20the%20result%20of%20tackling%20this%20resistance%20of%20donors%20and%20to%20incentivise%20them%20to%20use%20clean%20money%20through%20official%20banking%20channels%20while%20maintaining%20the%20confidentiality%20of%20their%20names.%20If%20this%20confidentiality%2C%20which%20is%20the%20heart%20and%20soul%20of%20the%20scheme%20and%20necessary%20to%20achieve%20the%20object%20of%20utilizing%20clean%20money%20for%20political%20donations%2C%20is%20removed%2C%20the%20scheme%20will%20become%20redundant%20and%20the%20country%20would%20go%20back%20to%20the%20era%20where%20donations%20to%20political%20parties%20were%20substantially%20made%20in%20cash%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20submitted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20that%20all%20arguments%20of%20the%20petitioners%20regarding%20the%20right%20to%20know%20and%20the%20necessity%20of%20transparency%20need%20to%20be%20examined%20from%20the%20above%20perspective.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20surprising%20claim%2C%20Mehta%20wondered%20what%20might%20be%20gained%20only%20by%20making%20known%20who%20the%20donors%20are.%20Confidentiality%20of%20those%20paying%20political%20parties%20and%20the%20parties%20benefitting%20from%20them%20strikes%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20clean%20political%20funding%20and%20healthy%20democratic%20practices.%20But%20Mehta%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHow%20the%20citizens%20would%20gain%20by%20going%20back%20to%20the%20earlier%20regime%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20the%20present%20scheme%2C%20though%20absolutely%20transparent%20and%20operating%20through%20the%20official%20channel%2C%20is%20declared%20to%20be%20bad%20merely%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20the%20donor%20and%20donee%20remain%20confidential.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20stressed%20that%20the%20elements%20of%20anonymity%20and%20the%20privacy%20of%20information%20are%20crucial%20to%20encourage%20and%20popularise%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELive%20Law%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reports%20that%20Justice%20Khanna%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20two%20aspects.%20One%2C%20whether%20by%20giving%20confidentiality%20to%20a%20donor%20you%20ensure%20a%20greater%20public%20interest%20is%20served.%20Second%2C%20is%20selective%20confidentiality.%20What%20happens%20is%20the%20person%20in%20power%20can%20have%20access%20to%20it.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20judge%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20confidentiality%20%5Bof%20donor%5D%20is%20given%2C%20how%20do%20we%20ensure%20what%20was%20called%20quid%20pro%20quo%20%E2%80%93%20how%20do%20we%20ensure%20that%20this%20is%20checked%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20this%2C%20Mehta%20said%20there%20is%20confidentiality%20as%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20maintains%20complete%20confidentiality.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20cannot%20find%20out%20whether%20my%20learned%20friend%20has%20given%20to%20A%20party%20or%20B.%20That%20I%20will%20show%20from%20the%20scheme.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FLiveLawIndia%2Fstatus%2F1719663811320598838%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20ultimately%2C%20you%20have%20to%20trust%20somewhere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3E%20LiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20cites%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMehta%20spent%20considerable%20time%20arguing%20that%20there%20would%20be%20no%20%3Cem%3Equid%20pro%20quo%3C%2Fem%3E%20between%20the%20party%20in%20government%20and%20the%20way%20electoral%20bonds%20have%20been%20devised%20and%20that%20the%20party%20in%20power%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20know%20who%20is%20donating%20to%20whom.%20The%2015-day%20window%20for%20encashing%20bonds%20was%20also%20justified%20on%20the%20same%20ground%2C%20as%20not%20allowing%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98quid%20pro%20quo%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20this%2C%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CRetribution%20is%20not%20avoided%20by%20the%20scheme.%20I%E2%80%99ll%20tell%20you%20the%20simple%20reason.%20Under%20the%20Companies%20Act%2C%20now%20modified%2C%20a%20company%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20disclose%20to%20which%20political%20party%20it%20has%20contributed.%20But%20it%20has%20to%20show%20how%20much%20it%20has%20contributed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20went%20on%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%20a%20company%20says%20I%E2%80%99ve%20contributed%20400%20crore%20this%20FY.%20Now%2C%20the%20party%20in%20power%20knows%20how%20much%20has%20come%20to%20it%20in%20terms%20of%20Electoral%20Bonds%20from%20that%20company.%E2%80%9D%20SG%20Mehta%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20can%20never%20know.%E2%80%9D%20The%20CJI%20said%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FLiveLawIndia%2Fstatus%2F1719650602739998892%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20the%20party%20of%20course%20knows.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECJI%20Chandrachud%20asked%20why%20the%20Election%20Commission%20was%20not%20the%20nodal%20entity%20to%20clean%20up%20election%20finances.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20if%20you%20really%20wanted%20to%20have%20that%20scheme%20and%20have%20a%20level%20playing%20field%2C%20then%20all%20these%20donations%20should%20be%20given%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20which%20would%20then%20be%20distributed%20on%20an%20equitable%20basis!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20this%2C%20Mehta%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThen%20nothing%20will%20come%20and%20everything%20will%20be%20by%20cash.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FLiveLawIndia%2Fstatus%2F1719666185267245127%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CJI%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99re%20absolutely%20right!%20That%20shows%20us%20the%20motivation%20for%20these%20donations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bench%20will%20resume%20hearings%20tomorrow%20on%20day%20three.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20an%20electoral%20bond%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20electoral%20bond%20is%20like%20a%20promissory%20note%20or%20bearer%20bond%20which%20can%20be%20purchased%20by%20any%20individual%2C%20company%2C%20firm%20or%20association%20of%20persons%20provided%20the%20person%20or%20body%20is%20a%20citizen%20of%20India%20or%20incorporated%20or%20established%20in%20India.%20Bonds%20of%20denominations%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%2C%20Rs%2C%2010%2C000%2C%20Rs%201%20lakh%2C%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20and%20Rs%201%20crore%20can%20be%20purchased.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bonds%20are%20issued%20specifically%20to%20contribute%20funds%20to%20political%20parties.%20The%20Finance%20Act%20which%20came%20up%20with%20electoral%20bonds%20was%20controversially%20passed%20as%20a%20Money%20Bill%20to%20bypass%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%E2%80%99s%20assent.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%20did%20not%20have%20control%20over%20the%20upper%20house%20to%20see%20that%20it%20was%20passed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EElectoral%20bonds%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20making%20political%20funding%20opaque%20and%20non-transparent.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sale%20of%20bonds%20has%20been%20skewed%20so%20far%20in%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20favour.%20The%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%2C%20which%20analysed%20donations%20received%20by%20political%20parties%20between%202016-17%20and%202021-22%2C%20found%20that%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-donations-electoral-bonds-thrice-other-parties-adr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBJP%20received%20more%20than%20thrice%20the%20total%20that%20all%20other%20parties%20received%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698847545000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F09172044%2FScreen-Shot-2021-03-09-at-5.20.25-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-donor-confidentiality-electoral-bonds-scheme%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20government%20has%20already%20come%20under%20fire%20for%20written%20submissions%20that%20said%20citizens%20had%20no%20fundamental%20right%20to%20know%20the%20sources%20of%20political%20funding.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-donor-confidentiality-electoral-bonds-scheme%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Tendulkar's%20Statue%20Unveiled%20At%20Wankhede%20Stadium%2C%20Where%20India%20Won%20WC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sachin%20Tendulkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F14-sachin-tendulkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESachin%20Tendulkar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20name%20that%20needs%20no%20introduction%20for%20Indian%20sports%20lovers.%20The%20cricket%20maestro%2C%20for%20decades%2C%20carried%20the%20hopes%20of%20billions%20on%20the%20cricket%20field.%20The%20numerous%20world%20records%2C%20including%20most%20international%20runs%20and%20centuries%2C%20is%20only%20one%20part%20of%20the%20Sachin%20Tendulkar's%20greatness.%20The%20respect%20that%20he%20commanded%20from%20his%20fellow%20teammates%20and%20rivals%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20his%20impact.%C2%A0Sachin%20Tendulkar%20got%20a%20fitting%20reward%20for%20his%20persistence%20when%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20won%202011%20World%20Cup%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%2C%20with%20the%20superstar%20being%20part%20of%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Sachin%20Tendulkar's%20life-sized%20statue%20has%20unveiled%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20India's%20World%20Cup%20clash%20against%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%2C%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20BCCI%20vice-president%20Rajeev%20Shukla%2C%20Mumbai%20Cricket%20Association%20(MCA)%20President%20Amol%20Kale%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20and%20Sachin's%20wife%20Anjali%20Tendulkar%2C%20daughter%20Sara%20Tendulkar%2C%20and%20brother%20Ajit%20Tendulkar%20were%20present%20during%20the%20unveiling%20of%20the%20statue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22de%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Statue%20of%20Cricket%20legend%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20unveiled%20at%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20in%20Mumbai.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FGbeURccO7X%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FGbeURccO7X%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FS0wRWttUnY%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FS0wRWttUnY%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1719693069019476426%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%201%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20statue%20is%20dedicated%20to%2050%20years%20of%20Tendulkar's%20life%20and%20has%20been%20installed%20by%20the%20MCA%20near%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20Stand%20at%20the%20stadium%2C%20and%20it%20was%20unveiled%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESudhir%20Kumar%20Chaudhary%2C%20team%20India's%20supporter%20and%20a%20fan%20of%20Sachin%2C%20was%20also%20present%20during%20the%20ceremony.%20He%20blew%20a%20conch%20shell%20and%20waved%20the%20Indian%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESachin%20is%20considered%20as%20the%20greatest%20batter%20to%20have%20played%20the%20game.%20With%2034%2C357%20runs%20in%20664%20international%20appearances%20at%20an%20average%20of%2048.52%2C%20Sachin%20is%20the%20highest%20run-scorer%20in%20international%20cricket.%20He%20has%20scored%20100%20centuries%20and%20164%20half-centuries%2C%20most%20in%20international%20cricket.%20He%20is%20the%20only%20player%20to%20have%20a%20century%20of%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%2018%2C426%20runs%20in%20ODIs%20and%2015%2C921%20runs%20in%20Tests%2C%20Sachin%20also%20has%20the%20highest%20runs%20in%20both%20formats.%20He%20is%20the%20first%20player%20to%20hit%20an%20ODI%20double%20hundred%20and%20to%20have%20played%20200%20Test%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20has%20201%20international%20wickets%20to%20his%20name%2C%20making%20him%20a%20very%20useful%20part-time%20spin%20bowling%20option.%20With%20a%20total%20of%20664%20international%20appearances%2C%20he%20is%20the%20most-capped%20player%20of%20all%20time.%20He%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20Team%20which%20won%20the%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESachin%20has%20played%20six%20IPL%20seasons%20from%202008-2013%2C%20all%20for%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20where%20he%20has%20scored%20a%20total%20of%202334%20runs%20in%2078%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2034.84.%20Sachin%20has%2013%20fifties%20and%20one%20hundred%20under%20his%20belt%2C%20hitting%2029%20sixes%20and%20295%20fours%20with%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20119.82.%20He%20won%20the%202013%20edition%20of%20the%20tournament%20with%20the%20franchise%20as%20a%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESachin's%20best%20performance%20came%20in%20IPL%202010.%20He%20scored%20618%20runs%20in%2015%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2047.53%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20132.61.%20He%20scored%20five%20fifties%20that%20season%20and%20his%20best%20individual%20score%20was%2089*.%20He%20won%20the%20'Orange%20Cap'%20that%20season.%20MI%20finished%20as%20runners-up%20that%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698847380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fhjl8ti4g_sachin-wc_625x300_01_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fsachin-tendulkars-statue-unveiled-at-wankhede-stadium-where-india-won-the-2011-cricket-world-cup-watch-4535912%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sachin%20Tendulkar's%20life-sized%20statue%20has%20unveiled%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20India's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20clash%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A134%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fsachin-tendulkars-statue-unveiled-at-wankhede-stadium-where-india-won-the-2011-cricket-world-cup-watch-4535912%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fsachin-tendulkars-statue-unveiled-at-wankhede-stadium-where-india-won-the-2011-cricket-world-cup-watch-4535912%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fsachin-tendulkars-statue-unveiled-at-wankhede-stadium-where-india-won-the-2011-cricket-world-cup-watch-4535912%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMaratha%20Reservation%20Without%20Touching%20Existing%20Quotas%26quot%3B%3A%20Eknath%20Shinde%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20the%20all-party%20meeting%20held%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%20decided%20that%20reservation%20should%20be%20given%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community%20without%20tampering%20with%20the%20existing%20quotas%20of%20other%20communities%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20n%20Mumbai%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20also%20appealed%20a