20some%20errors.%20We%20want%20to%20avoid%20a%20repetition%20of%20this%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shinde%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaking%20an%20appeal%20to%20Jarange%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20he%20should%20trust%20the%20government's%20efforts.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20of%20some%20violent%20incidents%2C%20the%20common%20man%20should%20not%20have%20any%20safety%20concerns.%20The%20entire%20Maratha%20community%20should%20support%20the%20state%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698847260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fvsec1ssc_eknath-shinde-devendra-fadnavis-ani_625x300_01_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-reservation-without-touching-existing-quotas-eknath-shinde-4534809%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20the%20all-party%20meeting%20held%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%20decided%20that%20reservation%20should%20be%20given%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community%20without%20tampering%20with%20the%20existing%20quotas%20of%20other%20communities%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-reservation-without-touching-existing-quotas-eknath-shinde-4534809%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-reservation-without-touching-existing-quotas-eknath-shinde-4534809%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-reservation-without-touching-existing-quotas-eknath-shinde-4534809%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20tells%20Sky%20News%20AI%20is%20a%20'risk'%20to%20humanity%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698847140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-elon-musk-ai-summit_6344203.jpg%3F20231101140730%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Felon-musk-tells-sky-news-ai-is-a-risk-to-humanity-12998024%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20has%20told%20Sky%20News%20that%20AI%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Brisk%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20the%20billionaire%20joins%20world%20leaders%20and%20tech%20bosses%20at%20a%20UK%20safety%20summit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A341%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Felon-musk-tells-sky-news-ai-is-a-risk-to-humanity-12998024%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Felon-musk-tells-sky-news-ai-is-a-risk-to-humanity-12998024%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Felon-musk-tells-sky-news-ai-is-a-risk-to-humanity-12998024%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20Need%20for%20a%20National%20Security%20Strategy%20Cannot%20Be%20Ignored%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F25161451%2F27440629405_563f1699dc_k.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20is%20a%20section%20of%20the%20keynote%20speech%20delivered%20by%20the%20author%20on%20October%2025%2C%202023%2C%20at%20the%20launch%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20National%20Security%20Challenges%2C%20%3Cem%3Ea%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Evolume%C2%A0edited%20by%20N.N.%20Vohra%2C%20at%20the%20India%20International%20Centre%20in%20New%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20have%20been%20at%20least%20three%20attempts%20so%20far%20that%20I%20know%20of%20to%20produce%20a%20national%20security%20strategy%20for%20India.%20In%20each%20case%20the%20hesitation%20came%20not%20from%20the%20professionals%2C%20in%20or%20out%20of%20uniform%2C%20but%20from%20the%20political%20levels.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20sense%2C%20but%20cannot%20prove%2C%20that%20they%20do%20not%20wish%20their%20hands%20to%20be%20tied%2C%20since%20strategy%20is%20essentially%20an%20ends%20and%20means%20problem%20and%20a%20NSS%20would%20need%20to%20be%20resourced.%20The%20major%20advantage%2C%20to%20my%20mind%2C%20of%20an%20NSS%2FNSP%20%5Bnational%20security%20policy%5D%20would%20be%20the%20accountability%20that%20it%20would%20introduce%20into%20the%20management%20of%20defence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECDS%20and%20higher%20defence%20management%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20286px)%2085vw%2C%20286px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01174551%2F41PeAEUCysL._SY445_SX342_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22286%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01174551%2F41PeAEUCysL._SY445_SX342_.jpg%20286w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01174551%2F41PeAEUCysL._SY445_SX342_-193x300.jpg%20193w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682986%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22445%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20National%20Security%20Challenges%2C%E2%80%99%20Primus%20Books%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20fundamental%20issue%20revealed%20in%20the%20book%20on%20the%20conception%20of%20the%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Staff%E2%80%99s%20role%20and%20the%20degree%20to%20which%20it%20is%20operational%20or%20advisory.%20Both%20points%20of%20view%20are%20represented%20here%2C%20and%20it%20is%20for%20the%20reader%20to%20make%20up%20his%20mind.%20The%20record%20of%20other%20countries%20at%20very%20different%20levels%20of%20development%20and%20in%20very%20different%20situations%20can%20not%20be%20compared%20with%20India%2C%20and%20this%20book%20avoids%20falling%20into%20that%20trap.%20But%20we%20still%20need%20to%20find%20our%20own%20way%20on%20the%20issue.%20Today%20the%20CDS%E2%80%99%20charter%20includes%20what%20the%20Chairman%20Joint%20Chiefs%20of%20Staff%20does%20in%20the%20US%2C%20(as%20the%20principal%20military%20advisor%20to%20the%20President%2C%20the%20Secretary%20Defence%20and%20the%20NSC)%2C%20and%20is%20also%20the%20Secretary%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Military%20Affairs%2C%20a%20secretarial%20function%2C%20and%20is%20supposed%20to%20drive%20our%20military%20reform.%20His%20operational%20role%20is%20still%20unclear.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20larger%20issue%20of%20the%20role%20of%20the%20multiple%20institutions%20that%20we%20have%20created%20to%20deal%20with%20national%20defence.%20What%20of%20the%20National%20Security%20Council%2C%20its%20secretariat%20and%20the%20NSA%2C%20and%20their%20relationship%20to%20the%20new%20CDS%2C%20Department%20of%20Military%20Affairs%3Cbr%3E%20and%20existing%20institutions%20like%20the%20Chiefs%20of%20Staff%20Committee%3F%20We%20have%20now%20had%20two%20and%20a%20half%20decades%20experience%20of%20the%20first%20NSC%20in%20a%20parliamentary%20democracy.%20It%20is%20time%20for%20us%20to%20clarify%20the%20the%20precise%20operational%20and%20advisory%20roles%20that%20the%20mix%20of%20institutions%20now%20play%2C%20and%20how%20they%20relate%20to%20each%20other.%20I%20say%20this%20because%20a%20clear%20chain%20of%20command%20is%20essential%20if%20we%20are%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20security%20situation%20facing%20us.%20Besides%2C%20uncertainty%20in%20this%20respect%20affects%20deterrence%20of%20our%20adversaries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20a%20full-fledged%20NSP%20may%20be%20difficult%2C%20it%20is%20time%20for%20a%20white%20paper%20from%20the%20government%2C%20setting%20out%20its%20thinking%20on%20these%20issues%20and%20the%20path%20forward.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJointness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20surprisingly%2C%20this%20was%20a%20subject%20that%20was%20universally%20supported%2C%20but%20each%20one%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20different%20idea%20of%20what%20it%20should%20mean.%20Some%20use%20it%20as%20only%20meaning%20integration%20of%20the%20uniformed%20services%2C%20others%20also%20include%20jointness%20between%20civilians%20and%20uniformed%20personnel.%20Both%20are%20essential%2C%20and%20lacking%20in%20our%20present%20arrangements.%20Mr%20Vohra%20makes%20the%20very%20valid%20point%20that%20there%20has%20to%20be%20a%20national%20defence%20doctrine%20which%20enables%20the%20services%20to%20undertake%20joint%20planning%20and%20fully%20integrated%205-10%20year%20defence%20plans.%20Without%20these%2C%20gaps%20in%20preparedness%20will%20only%20grow.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20CDS%20was%20very%20committed%20to%20introducing%20jointness%20in%20the%20working%20of%20the%20services%20and%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20integrated%20theatre%20commands.%20We%20hear%20less%20about%20this%20today.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETheaterisation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20probably%20the%20most%20contentious%20of%20the%20topics%20discussed.%20It%20is%20also%20something%20that%20is%20essential%20if%20we%20are%20to%20prevail%20over%20adversaries%20with%20better%20inner%20lines%20of%20communication%20and%2For%20technological%20and%20logistical%20advantages%20over%20us.%20There%20is%20a%20fascinating%20discussion%20in%20the%20record%20of%20the%20discussions%20among%20panelists%20on%20higher%20defence%20management%20reforms%20(page%2075)%20which%20makes%20clear%20the%20different%20points%20of%20view%20between%20the%20services.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20no%20country%20that%20I%20am%20aware%20of%20has%20jointness%20and%20theaterisation%20come%20about%20by%20consensus%20among%20all%20the%20stakeholders%2C%20particularly%20among%20those%20in%20uniform.%20Whether%20it%20was%20the%201986%20Goldwater-Nichols%20Act%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20US%2C%20or%20reform%20in%20the%20UK%20military%2C%20or%20the%202015%20PLA%20reforms%20which%20drew%20on%20US%20models%2C%20reform%20was%20widely%20recognised%20as%20needed%20but%20its%20shape%20was%20finally%20decided%20on%20and%20enforced%20by%20a%20decisive%20political%20leadership.%20The%20Goldwater-Nichols%20Act%20of%201986%20was%20a%20response%20to%20the%20US%20experience%20of%20the%20Vietnam%20War%20and%20changed%20the%20way%20US%20services%20interact.%20The%20services%20themselves%20%E2%80%9Corganise%2C%20train%20and%20equip%E2%80%9D%20forces%20for%20use%20by%20combatant%20commanders%20(CCDRs)%2C%20and%20the%20service%20chiefs%20no%20longer%20exercise%20any%20operational%20control%20over%20their%20forces.%20It%20built%20on%20the%201958%20Defence%20Reorganisation%20Act%20which%20took%20the%20services%20out%20of%20the%20loop%20and%20empowered%20the%20combatant%20commands.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20each%20case%20there%20was%20resistance%20and%20considerable%20pushback%2C%20but%20the%20results%20in%20terms%20of%20effectiveness%20have%20far%20outweighed%20the%20unforeseen%20and%20negative%20consequences.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERole%20of%20civilians%2C%20reform%20of%20MOD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20book%20also%20makes%20clear%20the%20differences%20between%20civilian%20and%20service%20attitudes%20to%20the%20role%20of%20MOD%20and%20the%20new%20DMA%2C%20and%20to%20how%20to%20integrate%20the%20different%20skills%20that%20uniformed%20personnel%20and%20civilians%20bring%20to%20decision-making%20on%20defence%20policy.%20There%20is%20a%20common%20plea%20in%20this%20volume%20for%20accountability%20and%20professionalism%20in%20the%20running%2C%20manning%20and%20operation%20of%20the%20MOD%20and%20other%20national%20security%20institutions.%20Incidentally%2C%20Goldwater-Nichols%20in%20the%20US%20resulted%20in%20the%20Navy%20building%20and%20fortifying%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwall%E2%80%9D%20between%20the%20Department%20of%20Navy%E2%80%99s%20military-run%20requirements%20process%20and%20the%20civilian-run%20acquisition%20process%20%E2%80%93%20a%20divide%20inimical%20to%20the%20efficient%20and%20effective%20support%20of%20military%20forces%20and%20antithetical%20to%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20legislation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20We%20have%20to%20ensure%20that%20we%20do%20not%20make%20the%20same%20mistake.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGeneral%20Rawat%20in%20his%20contribution%20argues%20that%20in%20an%20era%20of%20total%20war%20we%20need%20the%20involvement%20of%20the%20entire%20society%20in%20our%20national%20defence.%20This%20is%20unexceptionable%20as%20a%20sentiment.%20But%20it%20does%20raise%20the%20larger%20question%20of%20whether%20the%20answer%20is%20to%20militarise%20society%20or%20civilianise%20(some%20would%20say%20civilise)%20the%20military.%20Europe%20has%20probably%20gone%20too%20far%20in%20one%20direction%2C%20Israel%20in%20the%20other.%20Civilianising%20the%20military%20opens%20them%20to%20politicisation%20and%20reduces%20their%20military%20efficacy.%20Militarising%20society%20produces%20and%20society%20on%20tenterhooks%2C%20prone%20to%20violence%20and%20does%20not%20necessarily%20produce%20security%2C%20as%20we%20see%20in%20the%20Levant.%20Neither%20is%20satisfactory.%20The%20quest%20for%20absolute%20security%20by%20one%20actor%20creates%20insecurity%20for%20most%20others.%20The%20issue%20is%20one%20of%20striking%20the%20right%20balance.%20Of%20respecting%20the%20laws%20of%20war%20while%20ensuring%20deterrence%20and%20the%20capability%20to%20prevail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20thing%20that%20I%20would%20have%20liked%20more%20of%20in%20the%20book%20is%20a%20detailed%20discussion%20of%20internal%20security%20and%20its%20relation%20to%20national%20defence.%20Ajay%20Sahni%20has%20an%20excellent%20chapter%20on%20how%20internal%20security%20impacts%20national%20defence%2C%20describing%20the%20effects%20of%20growing%20inequality%2C%20the%20erosion%20of%20the%20integrity%20and%20autonomy%20of%20state%20institutions%2C%20and%20other%20recent%20phenomena.%20The%20spread%20of%20lawlessness%20and%20fraught%20centre-state%20relations%20mean%20that%20internal%20security%20increasingly%20impinges%20on%20our%20national%20defence.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMr%20Vohra%20makes%20some%20pointed%20suggestions%2C%20based%20on%20his%20vast%20experience%2C%20for%20MHA%20to%20be%20relieved%20of%20its%20non-security%20related%20tasks%2C%20redesigned%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Internal%20Security%20Affairs%2C%20and%20manned%20by%20trained%20personnel%20deployed%20on%20long%20tenures.%20As%20Mr%20Vohra%20notes%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20progressive%20increase%20in%20threats%20to%20internal%20security%20(page%204)%2C%20which%20might%20have%20merited%20a%20separate%20chapter%20in%20itself%2C%20for%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20a%20duty%20under%20the%20constitution%20to%20protect%20every%20state%20against%20internal%20disturbance%20and%20external%20aggression.%20But%20perhaps%20that%20might%20be%20a%20subsequent%20exercise%20to%20produce%20another%20such%20volume.%20To%20my%20mind%20the%20distinction%20between%20internal%20and%20external%20security%20is%20being%20blurred%20in%20cyberspace%2C%20across%20porous%20borders%2C%20and%20by%20increasing%20economic%20dependencies.%20It%20is%20that%20linkage%20that%20siloed%20thinking%20prevents%20us%20from%20seeing%2C%20and%20that%20creates%20vulnerabilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20cannot%20stress%20too%20strongly%20the%20need%20for%20us%20to%20take%20heed%20of%20what%20this%20book%20says%20and%20to%20act%20rapidly%20on%20these%20issues%20of%20external%20security%20management.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20say%20so%20for%20three%20reasons%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E1.%20Though%20India%20today%20faces%20no%20existential%20threat%20from%20abroad%2C%20the%20external%20situation%20has%20worsened%20considerably%20in%20the%20last%20decade%20and%20a%20half.%20The%20task%20of%20Indian%20security%20professionals%20is%20to%20create%20an%20enabling%20environment%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20transformation%20into%20a%20modern%2C%20prosperous%2C%20and%20secure%20country%20where%20every%20Indian%20has%20the%20opportunity%20to%20achieve%20their%20potential.%20That%20requires%20us%20to%20continue%20to%20deter%20our%20adversaries%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20war%20as%20far%20as%20possible%20and%2C%20where%20that%20proves%20not%20possible%2C%20to%20increase%20the%20intervals%20between%20wars.%20While%20we%20have%20achieved%20that%20for%20several%20decades%2C%20the%20task%20of%20deterring%20our%20adversaries%20has%20now%20got%20harder%20with%20a%20slowing%20world%20economy%2C%20rising%20great%20power%20rivalry%2C%20and%20developments%20in%20technology.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELet%20me%20elaborate.%20Technology%20has%20changed%20and%20expanded%20the%20battlefield%20and%20nullified%20some%20of%20our%20advantages%20on%20the%20LAC%3B%20great%20power%20rivalry%20enables%20Pakistan%20to%20again%20begin%20charging%20strategic%20rent%20internationally%2C%20something%20she%20was%20unable%20to%20do%20for%20a%20few%20years%3B%20and%2C%20when%20our%20economy%20is%20more%20than%20ever%20before%20integrated%20with%20a%20slowing%20world%20economy%2C%20there%20will%20be%20less%20available%20for%20the%20self-strengthening%2C%20military%20modernisation%2C%20and%20defence%20reform%20that%20we%20all%20agree%20is%20required.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E2.%20Secondly%2C%20deterrence%20has%20broken%20down%20along%20the%20LAC%20with%20China%2C%20our%20major%20security%20preoccupation.%20What%20happened%20in%202020%20in%20the%20western%20sector%2C%20and%20subsequent%20developments%20including%20local%20disengagement%20in%20some%20areas%2C%20is%20evident%20to%20all%20in%20satellite%20pictures%20available%20to%20the%20public.%20These%20do%20not%20suggest%20that%20deterrence%20has%20been%20restored.%20Instead%2C%20we%20are%20in%20a%20political%20impasse%20and%20a%20military%20standoff%2C%20however%20described%2C%20with%20over%20100%2C000%20troops%20along%20the%20LAC%20in%20the%20western%20sector%20and%20infrastructure%20construction%20continuing%20apace.%20The%20LAC%20is%20live.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20nothing%20to%20suggest%20that%20we%20are%20making%20progress%20towards%20either%20stabilising%20the%20border%20with%20China%2C%20or%20preventing%20China%20from%20using%20the%20threat%20of%20action%20on%20the%20border.%20The%20commitment%20of%20scarce%20resources%20to%20the%20standoff%20itself%20represents%20an%20opportunity%20cost%20for%20our%20national%20defence.%20It%20also%20poses%20serious%20reputational%20damage%20to%20us.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E3.%20Thirdly%2C%20half-done%20reform%20creates%20new%20vulnerabilities%20without%20solving%20old%20ones.%20You%20cannot%20cross%20a%20chasm%20in%20two%20leaps.%20We%20are%20today%20in%20a%20situation%20where%20many%20of%20the%20reforms%20begun%20by%20the%20former%20CDS%2C%20General%20Bipin%20Rawat%2C%20who%20has%20a%20well-argued%20contribution%20in%20this%20volume%2C%20are%20incomplete.%20Operational%20roles%20need%20to%20be%20clear%20at%20every%20level%2C%20from%20the%20CDS%20and%20NSA%20downward.%20Issues%20that%20we%20regard%20as%20internal%20to%20us%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Agniveer%20recruitment%20pattern%2C%20have%20external%20ramifications%20in%20our%20dealings%20with%20Nepal%20that%20need%20to%20be%20sorted%20out.%C2%A0%20Other%20issues%20have%20been%20pending%20or%20hanging%20fire%20from%20before%20the%20CDS%20was%20appointed.%20The%20fate%20of%20the%20mountain%20strike%20corps%2C%20approved%20by%20the%20CCS%20in%202013%2C%20is%20one%20such%20example%2C%20as%20is%20the%20limbo%20in%20which%20the%20National%20Defence%20University%20awaits%2C%20and%20the%20integration%20of%20combat%20air%20in%20the%20Army.%20There%20is%20a%20long%20list%20of%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20done.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20common%20thread%20in%20all%20these%20reasons%20for%20change%20is%20the%20need%20to%20enhance%20deterrence%20of%20our%20potential%20adversaries.%20If%20their%20assertive%20behaviour%20is%20anything%20to%20go%20by%2C%20that%20deterrence%20has%20been%20degraded%20and%20its%20credibility%20needs%20to%20be%20restored.%20That%20is%20why%20reform%20of%20our%20defence%20management%20and%20armed%20forces%20so%20essential.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20has%20happened%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20since%20October%207%20is%20an%20object%20lesson%20on%20how%20dangerous%20complacency%20and%20hubris%20can%20be%20and%20how%20devastating%20their%20consequences.%20We%20also%20see%20in%20the%20Levant%20how%20hard%20it%20is%20to%20restore%20deterrence%20once%20it%20is%20degraded%2C%20and%20how%20military%20options%20can%20only%20go%20so%20far%20without%20a%20clear%20political%20goal%20and%20component%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20terrorist%20or%20other%20attacks%20and%20threats.%20There%20are%20clearly%20lessons%20for%20us%20to%20be%20learnt%20from%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20Levant.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20our%20overall%20goal%20of%20transforming%20India%20remains%2C%20and%20will%20need%20to%20be%20defended%20in%20new%20ways%20in%20the%20years%20to%20come.%20This%20book%20offers%20us%20pathways%20forward%20to%20do%20so.%20Indeed%2C%20though%20I%20have%20spoken%20of%20differences%20of%20opinion%20expressed%20in%20the%20book%2C%20I%20was%20impressed%20by%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20authors%20from%20different%20services%20and%20varied%20experiences%20still%20agree%20on%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20done.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20an%20apocryphal%20World%20War%20I%20story%20about%20the%20difference%20between%20German%20and%20Austrian%20attitudes%20to%20war.%20When%20the%20German%20commander%20reported%20that%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20eastern%20front%20was%20%E2%80%98serous%20but%20not%20hopeless%E2%80%99%20the%20Austrian%20reported%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%98hopeless%20but%20not%20serious.%E2%80%99%20Our%20situation%20is%20serious%20but%20not%20hopeless%2C%20despite%20the%20precarious%20international%20environment%2C%20particularly%20in%20our%20neighbourhood%2C%20and%20the%20pressing%20need%20for%20reform%20and%20modernisation%20of%20our%20defence.%20This%20book%20suggests%20that%20we%20can%20manage%20the%20situation%20if%20we%20reform.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShivshankar%20Menon%20was%20India%E2%80%99s%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20from%202010%20to%20May%202014.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698846601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F25161451%2F27440629405_563f1699dc_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Findias-need-for-a-national-security-strategy-cannot-be-ignored%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20a%20full-fledged%20NSP%20may%20be%20difficult%2C%20it%20is%20time%20for%20a%20white%20paper%20from%20the%20government%2C%20setting%20out%20its%20thinking%20on%20these%20issues%20and%20the%20path%20forward.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Findias-need-for-a-national-security-strategy-cannot-be-ignored%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThe%20Irony%20Is%20That...%26quot%3B%3A%20Musk%20After%20Tesla%20Wins%20Trial%20Involving%20Fatal%20Crash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETesla%20on%20Tuesday%20was%20cleared%20by%20a%20court%20in%20the%202019%20fatal%20Model%203%20crash%20that%20took%20place%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20US%2C%20involving%20its%20advanced%20driver-assistance%20system%2C%20Autopilot.%20The%20case%20was%20filed%20by%20tw