ay%20is%20also%20being%20celebrated%20as%20%E2%80%98National%20Unity%20Day%E2%80%99%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20celebrations%20by%20the%20UT%20administration%20were%20to%20commemorate%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20designation%20as%20a%20Union%20territory%20on%20October%2031%2C%202019.%20Political%20parties%20questioned%20the%20logic%20behind%20such%20celebrations%20when%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20assured%20that%20the%20UT%20status%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%20was%20only%20temporary%2C%20and%20it%20would%20be%20soon%20bestowed%20with%20full%20statehood%20again.%20Tuesday%E2%80%99s%20celebrations%20by%20the%20administration%20came%20days%20before%20the%20scheduled%20verdict%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20the%20Article%20370%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnew-special-status-thrust-on-jk-is-an-abuse-of-the-constitution-and-a-danger-to-the-republic%5C%22%3ENew%20Special%20Status%20Thrust%20on%20J%26amp%3BK%20Is%20an%20Abuse%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20a%20Danger%20to%20the%20Republic%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Insult%20to%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99%3A%20Political%20parties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20celebrations%2C%20the%20administration%20held%20a%20series%20of%20events%20across%20districts%20and%20in%20both%20capital%20cities%20of%20Srinagar%20and%20Jammu.%20From%20students%20to%20government%20employees%20to%20commoners%2C%20the%20administration%20roped%20in%20people%20from%20all%20walks%20of%20life%20to%20highlight%2C%20what%20it%20described%20as%20%E2%80%9Cprogress%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20Union%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01162037%2FF9xkg8vaMAAEl1v.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01162037%2FF9xkg8vaMAAEl1v.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01162037%2FF9xkg8vaMAAEl1v-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01162037%2FF9xkg8vaMAAEl1v-1024x682.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682947%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22799%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECelebrations%20by%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20administration%20to%20mark%20%E2%80%98UT%20Foundation%20Day%E2%80%99%20on%20October%2031%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40OfficeOfLGJandK%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20celebrations%20by%20the%20administration%20raised%20eyebrows%20of%20people%2C%20for%20it%20was%20the%20first%20time%20after%20October%2031%2C%202019%2C%20such%20celebrations%20were%20held.%20Even%20in%202019%2C%20the%20celebrations%20were%20a%20low-key%20affair%20and%20were%20confined%20to%20Raj%20Bhavan%20in%20Srinagar.%20The%20day%20in%202019%20marked%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20formal%20transition%20to%20Union%20territory%2C%20and%20G.C.%20Murmu%20took%20over%20as%20its%20first%20lieutenant%20governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolitical%20parties%20condemned%20celebrations%20by%20the%20administration.%20While%20Congress%20observed%20the%20day%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cblack%20day%E2%80%9D%2C%20other%20parties%20said%20that%20it%20amounted%20to%20rubbing%20salt%20in%20the%20wounds%20of%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20nothing%20to%20celebrate%20about%20the%20day.%20Should%20we%20celebrate%20the%20downgrading%20of%20our%20state%20or%20the%20snatching%20of%20our%20democratic%20rights%3F%20In%20reality%2C%20today%20is%20a%20day%20of%20mourning%20and%20sorrow%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20today%20is%20a%20black%20day%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20National%20Conference%20vice-president%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Omar%20Abdullah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20rubbing%20salt%20on%20our%20wounds.%20Were%20we%20asked%20before%20creating%20this%20UT%20or%20did%20we%20have%20a%20say%20in%20this%20decision%3F%20Did%20we%20benefit%20from%20this%20decision%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20leader%20and%20four-time%20legislator%20Muhammad%20Yosuf%20Tarigami%20said%20celebrating%20the%20day%20as%20%E2%80%9CUT%20Diwas%E2%80%9D%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20this%20can%20be%20a%20celebration%3F%20In%20parliament%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20assured%20the%20people%20that%20statehood%20would%20be%20restored%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20independence%2C%20no%20state%20was%20downgraded%20to%20a%20Union%20territory.%20Union%20territories%20are%20demanding%20statehood.%20The%20Leh%20Apex%20Body%20and%20Kargil%20Democratic%20Alliance%20from%20Ladakh%20are%20demanding%20full-fledged%20statehood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELed%20by%20their%20president%20Viqar%20Rasool%2C%20Congress%20party%20workers%20staged%20protests%20in%20Jammu%2C%20demanding%20restoration%20of%20statehood%20and%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Jammu%2C%20senior%20National%20Conference%20leader%20Rattan%20Lal%20Gupta%20said%20the%20BJP%20rubbed%20salt%20in%20the%20wounds%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20by%20celebrating%20the%20%E2%80%9CUT%20Foundation%20Day%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0He%20said%20that%20the%20party%20demeaned%20the%20glory%20of%20the%20Dogra%20community%20as%20it%20was%20on%20this%20day%20that%20the%20erstwhile%20J%26amp%3BK%20state%20was%20downgraded%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccut%20into%20pieces%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20message%20behind%20celebrations%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20could%20have%20been%20the%20reasons%20behind%20the%20administration%20celebrating%20%E2%80%98UT%20Foundation%20Day%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20first%20time%20after%202019%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20October%2C%2031%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20still%20remains%20a%20mystery.%20While%20some%20sections%20see%20it%20as%20an%20exercise%20by%20UT%20administration%20to%20showcase%2C%20what%20it%20says%2C%20its%20achievements%20in%20the%20past%20four%20years%2C%20others%20see%20a%20political%20message%3A%20that%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20statehood%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20restored%20in%20the%20near%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjammu-kashmir-without-elected-government-five-years%5C%22%3EJ%26amp%3BK%3A%20In%205%20Years%20Without%20Elected%20Govt%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Crown%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20Has%20Become%20a%20Khap%20Panchayat%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98UT%20Foundation%20Day%E2%80%99%20was%20observed%20ahead%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20much-awaited%20verdict%20in%20the%20Article%20370%20case.%20The%20judgment%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20pronounced%20in%20November-December%20as%20Justice%20Sanjay%20Kishan%20Kaul%2C%20one%20of%20the%20judges%20of%20the%20constitution%20bench%20that%20heard%20the%20Article%20370%20case%2C%20is%20attaining%20superannuation%20on%20November%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20worthwhile%20to%20mention%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20promised%20multiple%20times%20that%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20statehood%20will%20be%20restored%20at%20an%20appropriate%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20meeting%20with%20political%20parties%20from%20J%26amp%3BK%20on%20June%2024%2C%202021%2C%20Modi%20assured%20them%20that%20his%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20restoring%20statehood%20to%20J%26amp%3BK.%C2%A0On%20February%2013%20this%20year%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20that%20the%20statehood%20would%20be%20restored%20only%20afte