d%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20trust%20first.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20been%20planning%20since%202015.%20We%20worked%20with%20the%20girls%2C%20the%20boys%20and%20their%20parents%20and%20sensitised%20them%20%5Bto%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20girls%E2%80%99%20sports%20programme%5D.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20has%20also%20actively%20addressed%20common%20concerns%20raised%20by%20parents%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F162218%2Fuber-cab-women-safety%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregarding%20the%20safety%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20expenses%20of%20the%20girls%20participating%20in%20tournaments%20held%20in%20larger%20cities.%20Recognising%20these%20concerns%2C%20the%20programme%20takes%20responsibility%20for%20the%20girls%E2%80%99%20expenses%20and%20ensures%20their%20safety%20by%20arranging%20for%20accompanying%20coaches%20during%20their%20travel.%20In%20certain%20cases%2C%20the%20programme%20even%20covers%20medical%20expenses%20and%20provides%20first%20aid%20kits.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVivek%20emphasises%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20way%2C%20we%20address%20any%20doubts%20community%20members%20may%20have%20about%20the%20program%2C%20ensuring%20that%20their%20questions%20are%20answered%20satisfactorily.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMatthew%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20when%20I%20played%20rugby%20with%20young%20people%2C%20I%20believed%20that%20helping%20them%20secure%20jobs%20would%20lead%20to%20economic%20stability.%20However%2C%20we%20realised%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20ready%20for%20a%20structured%20work%20environment.%20This%20setback%20inspired%20our%20%E2%80%9CChildhood%20to%20Livelihood%E2%80%9D%20programme.%20We%20understood%20that%20getting%20them%20jobs%20was%20only%20half%20the%20battle%3B%20keeping%20them%20employed%20required%20equipping%20them%20with%20the%20right%20skills%20and%20guidance%20to%20enter%20the%20workforce.%20It%E2%80%99s%20where%20they%20grasp%20the%20value%20of%20work%2C%20learn%20skills%20beyond%20their%20chosen%20profession%2C%20and%20evolve%20into%20role%20models%2C%20actively%20breaking%20the%20cycle%20of%20poverty%20for%20their%20families%20and%20the%20entire%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20big%20part%20of%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation's%20work%20is%20to%20provide%20vocational%20skills'%20training%20to%20Indian%20kids%20to%20ensure%20a%20secure%20future.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055-768x768.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055-96x96.jpeg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333300%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20big%20part%20of%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20to%20provide%20vocational%20skills%20training%20to%20Indian%20kids%20to%20ensure%20a%20secure%20future.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Showed%20me%20the%20right%20path%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EVivek%20points%20to%20the%20example%20of%20Prachi%2C%20a%20young%20girl%20who%20had%20previously%20never%20left%20her%20village.%20Last%20year%20she%20travelled%20to%20a%20national%20athletic%20competition%20in%20Ranchi%2C%20Bihar.%20%E2%80%9CHer%20parents%20were%20in%20complete%20shock%20that%20a%20girl%20who%20never%20left%20the%20home%20before%20has%20performed%20in%20this%20kind%20of%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98If%20you%20had%20not%20tried%20with%20our%20child%2C%20she%20would%20never%20have%20reached%20this%20level.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20girl%20who%20has%20benefitted%20from%20Magic%20Bus%E2%80%99%20interventions%20is%2017-year-old%20Bittu%20Kumari.%20She%20joined%20the%20programme%20in%202017%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330978%2Fkamlesh-atwal-started-nanakmatta-public-school-uttarakhand-holistic-education-for-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20Class%208%20student%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20says%20she%20learned%20life%20skills%20through%20volleyball%20and%20kabaddi%20(volleyball%20has%20since%20been%20replaced%20with%20cricket).%20According%20to%20her%2C%20Magic%20Bus%20helped%20her%20make%20the%20optimum%20use%20of%20her%20talent%20as%20a%20kabaddi%20player.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20I%20am%20a%20state-level%20kabaddi%20player%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20play%20at%20the%20national%20level%20also%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20had%20not%20found%20Magic%20Bus%2C%20I%20would%20not%20have%20made%20it%20this%20far.%20They%20showed%20me%20the%20right%20path.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20process%2C%20she%20has%20gone%20from%20being%20scared%20to%20speak%20to%20people%20to%20having%20the%20confidence%20to%20speak%20to%20anyone.%20%E2%80%9CMagic%20Bus%20taught%20me%20communication%20skills%2C%20gave%20me%20confidence%2C%20taught%20me%20what%20is%20right%20and%20what%20is%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20Magic%20Bus%20appointed%20Bittu%20as%20one%20of%20their%20community%20coordinators.%20While%20her%20ambition%20is%20to%20become%20an%20IPS%20officer%2C%20she%20also%20plans%20to%20play%20kabaddi%20for%20as%20long%20as%20she%20can.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20give%20me%20full%20support.%20They%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98When%20my%20daughter%20is%20on%20the%20right%20track%2C%20why%20would%20I%20stop%20her%3F%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Matthew%2C%20these%20stories%20motivate%20him%20further.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20emotional%20aspect%20of%20our%20work%20reminds%20me%20of%20our%20mission%E2%80%99s%20importance%20and%20the%20need%20to%20stay%20rooted%20in%20the%20communities%20we%20serve.%20By%20understanding%20their%20struggles%20and%20empathising%20with%20their%20challenges%2C%20we%20ensure%20our%20programmes%20remain%20relevant%20and%20effective.%20This%20powerful%20motivation%20drives%20our%20commitment%20to%20doing%20right%20by%20them%20and%20striving%20for%20continuous%20improvement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20contributed%20by%20the%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698761468000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333285%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Using%20sports%20to%20teach%20crucial%20life%20skills%2C%20Magic%20Bus%20Foundation%20India%20is%20playing%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20impacting%204%2C00%2C000%20adolescent%20girls%20in%2022%20states.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Made%20Of%20Shipping%20Containers%2C%20Our%20Home%20Harvests%20the%20Sun%2C%20the%20Rain%20%26amp%3B%20Kitchen%20Waste%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHaving%20dedicated%20close%20to%2030%20years%20to%20talking%20about%20the%20environment%20and%20sustainability%2C%20Hyderabad-based%20M%20V%20Ramachan