he%20agricultural%20landscape%20of%20Bihar.%20While%20this%20recognition%20was%20an%20auspicious%20beginning%2C%20challenges%20persisted%20for%20small-scale%20farmers%2C%20who%20struggled%20to%20maximise%20their%20profits%20and%20access%20broader%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Manish%20Singh%2C%20a%20teacher%20by%20profession%2C%20hailing%20from%20a%20farming%20family%20in%20Sultangunj%20village%20in%20Bhagalpur%2C%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20plunge%20into%20agriculture.%20With%20a%20deep-rooted%20passion%20for%20farming%20and%20a%20vision%20to%20amplify%20the%20value%20of%20the%20produce%2C%20Manish%20embarked%20on%20a%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20having%20a%20GI%20tag%2C%20most%20farmers%20in%20the%20district%20were%20selling%20Katarni%20paddy%20at%20Rs%2030%20per%20kg.%20The%20challenge%2C%20Manish%20says%2C%20was%20that%20%E2%80%9Cfarmers%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20the%20value%20of%20the%20rice.%20Since%20we%20are%20all%20small%20farmers%2C%20we%20were%20not%20able%20to%20get%20the%20right%20price%20or%20find%20the%20right%20people%20to%20sell%20our%20products%20to.%E2%80%9D%20He%20knew%20collectivisation%20was%20the%20only%20way%20to%20ensure%20that%20farmers%20like%20himself%20are%20able%20to%20get%20the%20right%20value%20for%20their%20produce%2C%20Manish%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EManish%20led%20a%20group%20of%20farmers%20to%20form%20the%20Jardalu%20and%20Katarni%20Agro%20Producer%20Company%20Limited%2C%20a%20Farmer%20Producer%20Organisation%20(FPO)%2C%20in%20April%202023.%20Their%20journey%20was%20made%20possible%20through%20the%20support%20of%20Bayer%2C%20working%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Small%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Agri-Business%20Consortium%20(SFAC)%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20developed%20the%20concept%20of%20FPOs%20in%20the%20early%202000s%20to%20enable%20small%20and%20marginal%20farmers%20t