20her%20conservation%20work.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAnne-Wright-Award-1698675452.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAnne-Wright-Award-1698675452-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAnne-Wright-Award-1698675452-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAnne-Wright-Award-1698675452-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAnne-Wright-Award-1698675452-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333245%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDuring%20her%20life%2C%20Anne%20Wright%20received%20a%20myriad%20of%20awards%20for%20her%20conservation%20work.%20She%20was%20awarded%20the%20Order%20of%20Golden%20Ark%20by%20Prince%20Bernhard%20of%20Netherlands%20in%201979%2C%20%E2%80%98Most%20Excellent%20Order%20of%20the%20British%20Empire%E2%80%99%20(MBE)%20in%201983%2C%20and%20the%20Sanctuary%20Asia%20Lifetime%20Service%20Award%20in%202013.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMoreover%2C%20what%20strikes%20out%20the%20most%20to%20me%20is%20her%20ability%20to%20forge%20alliances%20over%20common%20cause%20across%20an%20incredibly%20diverse%20set%20of%20people%20and%20stakeholders%20%E2%80%94%20from%20forest%20officers%20to%20politicians%20in%20high%20offices%3B%20from%20businessmen%20to%20communities%20living%20around%20forests%3B%20from%20celebrities%20and%20global%20and%20national%20public%20figures%20to%20young%20school%20kids%3B%20and%20from%20naturalists%20to%20policymakers.%20She%20worked%20with%20everyone%20and%20brought%20them%20together%20for%20the%20cause%20of%20conservation%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Raza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20can%20think%20of%20very%20few%20people%2C%20perhaps%20none%2C%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20conserva